-events-july-2018%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3EChina's%20tensions%20with%20Washington%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20disrupting%20supply%20in%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20yet%20another%20thing%20is%20playing%20out%20that%20might%20even%20keep%20you%20from%20getting%20your%20holiday%20presents%20on%20time%20months%20from%20now%3A%20the%20climate%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20serious%20this%20summer%20because%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fenvironment%2Fhistoric-drought-hot-seas-slow-panama-canal-shipping-2023-08-21%2F%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fenvironment%2Fhistoric-drought-hot-seas-slow-panama-canal-shipping-2023-08-21%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Ehistoric%20drought%3C%2Fa%3E%20affecting%20rainfall%20that%20feeds%20into%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%20This%20has%20lowered%20the%20canal's%20water%20levels%20and%20limited%20the%20number%20and%20the%20weight%20of%20ships%20that%20can%20float%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20causing%20a%20buildup%20in%20the%20number%20of%20ships%20waiting%20to%20cross%20the%20waterway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDroughts%20aren't%20a%20new%20phenomenon%20at%20the%20Panama%20Canal%20%E2%80%94%20climate%20change%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fpanama-canal-tackles-climate-change-puzzle-too-little-rainwater-or-too-much-11624872601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunpredictable%20weather%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpanama-canal-drought-travel-ships-income-falling-el-nino-2023-8%5C%22%3Edry%20weather%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20worse%20this%20summer%2C%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22h