ote%2C%20though%2C%20that%20a%20strike%20could%20influence%20each%20automaker's%20earnings%20by%20%24400%20million%20to%20%24500%20million%20for%20each%20week%20of%20lost%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20automakers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautomakers-car-buyers-investors-inventory-strike-pricing-incentives-electric-vehicles-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efaced%20supply-chain%20constraints%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20with%20computer%20chips%2C%20that%20hindered%20vehicle%20production.%20Despite%20a%20lack%20of%20inventory%2C%20industry%20profits%20skyrocketed%2C%20even%20though%202022%20was%20the%20worst%20year%20for%20sales%20for%20the%20auto%20industry%20in%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20UAW%20strike%20could%20damage%20the%20Fed's%20progress%20in%20bringing%20inflation%20down%20to%20its%202%25%20target.%20Inflation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-inflation-economy-cpi-july-data-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewas%20about%203.2%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20of%20August.%20New-vehicle%20prices%20may%20increase%20nearly%202%25%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20two-week%20strike%2C%20the%20automotive-consulting%20firm%20J.D.%20Power%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos-transportation%2Fpotential-uaw-strike-could-cut-production-push-up-vehicle-prices-analysts-say-2023-09-11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInflation%20may%20stay%20on%20pace%20even%20if%20UAW%20quickly%20wins%20higher%20wages%2C%20given%20many%20auto%20workers%20did%20not%20see%20major%20wage%20gains%20earlier%20in%20the%20pandemic%20given%20they%20were%20locked%20into%20contracts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-09-10%2Feven-a-brief-uaw-strike-seen-causing-billions-in-damage-to-us-economy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22