ar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F14-sachin-tendulkar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESachin%20Tendulkar%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20achieve%20a%20sensational%20record%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20on%20Monday.%20The%2034-year-old%20became%20the%20fastest%20to%20reach%2013%2C000%20runs%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20as%20he%20reached%20the%20milestone%20in%20his%20267th%20innings.%20The%20world%20record%20previously%20belonged%20to%20legendary%20India%20batter%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%2C%20who%20achieved%20the%20feat%20in%20321%20innings%20but%20Kohli%20was%20able%20to%20shatter%20the%20existing%20record%20with%20a%20brilliant%20knock%20against%20Pakistan.%20Australia%20great%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ricky%20Ponting%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F348-ricky-ponting-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERicky%20Ponting%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20third%20in%20the%20list%20as%20he%20took%20341%20innings%20to%20score%2013%2C000%20ODI%20runs.%20%3Cstrong%3E(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Find-vs-pak-live-score-asia-cup-2023-india-vs-pakistan-match-live-updates-on-reserve-day-4378637%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%20vs%20Pakistan%3A%20Asia%20Cup%20Live%20updates%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20ultimately%20stayed%20unbeaten%20on%20122%20(94b)%20while%20KL%20Rahul%C2%A0%20ended%20on%20unbeaten%20111*%20(106b)%20as%20India%20scored%20a%20massive%20356%2F2%20in%2050%20overs%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20a%20crucial%20Super%204%20match.%20India%20ultimately%20won%20the%20match%20by%20a%20record%20228-run%20margin%20-%20their%20biggest%20win%20over%20Pakistan%20in%20terms%20of%20runs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20Virat%20Kohli's%20fourth%20successive%20century%20at%20the%20R%20Premadasa%20Stadium%20in%20Colombo.%20His%20scores%20from%20the%20last%20three%20matches%20at%20the%20venue%20read%20-%20128*(119b)%2C%20131(96b)%20and%20110*(116b).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20and%20KL%20Rahul%20also%20set%20a%20new%20Asia%20Cup%20(ODI)%20record%20as%20they%20stitched%20a%20233-run%20stand.%20They%20broke%20the%20record%20of%20Pakistan's%20Mohammad%20Hafeez%20and%20N%20Jamshed%2C%20who%20scored%20a%20224-run%20stand%20against%20India%20in%202012.%20Virat%20Kohli%20has%20now%20equalled%20Sri%20Lanka%20great%20Kumar%20Sangakkara's%20record%20of%20four%20centuries%20in%20Asia%20Cup.%20Only%20Sanath%20Jayasuriya%20(6)%20has%20more%20tons%20in%20the%20continental%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo's%20performance%20was%20praised%20by%20Shubman%20Gill.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20special%20for%20us.%20He%20(Rahul)%20was%20playing%20his%20first%20match%20after%20coming%20back%20from%20injury%20and%20to%20be%20able%20to%20score%20a%20century%20in%20these%20conditions%20was%20pretty%20magnificent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%20Virat%20Bhai%20also%20completed%20his%20century%20and%20got%20to%2013000%20runs%20which%20shows%20his%20great%20inspiration%20to%20all%20of%20us.%20The%20ball%20was%20doing%20a%20little%20bit%20in%20the%20initial%20period%20and%20they%20also%20bowled%20well%20with%20the%20new%20ball%2C%20but%20it%20was%20important%20for%20us%20to%20take%20them%20on%20and%20put%20the%20bad%20balls%20away%20to%20put%20the%20pressure%20back%20on%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20he%20(Shaheen)%20was%20trying%20to%20attack%20the%20wickets%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20show%20intent%2C%20worked%20for%20me%20yesterday.%20There's%20a%20bit%20of%20seam%20movement%20and%20once%20the%20ball%20gets%20older%20we%20have%20to%20mix%20it%20up%20with%20slower%20ones%2C%20I%20found%20it%20difficult%20when%20they%20were%20mixing%20up%20their%20length%20and%20pace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694462220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F1phnu1mg_kohli-ton-_625x300_11_S