for%20South%20Korea%20and%20the%20US%20to%20target%20North%20Korean%20artillery%20units%20hidden%20and%20sheltered%20from%20counterfire.%20But%20most%20experts%20assess%20that%20there%20would%20be%20a%20severe%20response%20from%20Seoul%20and%20Washington%20if%20North%20Korea%20followed%20through%20on%20its%20threats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20DPRK's%20daunting%20conventional%20capabilities%20%E2%80%94%20and%20increasingly%20threatening%20missile%20tests%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20quite%20clear%20if%20all%20of%20the%20nation's%20weapons%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20experts%20have%20said%20some%20of%20Kim's%20stockpiles%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnorth-korean-weapons-sought-by-putin-likely-shoddy-unreliable-analysts-2023-9%5C%22%3Eaging%20and%20ineffective%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-using-north-korean-rockets-against-russian-forces-2023-7%5C%22%3ENorth%20Korean-made%20rockets%20found%20in%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20%26quot%3Bunreliable%20and%20do%20crazy%20things%20sometimes.%26quot%3B%20The%20DPRK%20has%20previously%20denied%20accusations%20that%20it%20has%20been%20providing%20weapons%20to%20the%20Russian%20military.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222362%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22North%20Korea%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20observes%20artillery%20fire%20competition%20in%20North%20Korea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ff4a834b33390019f095d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221555%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENorth%20Korea%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20observes%20artillery%20fire%20competition%20in%20North%20Korea.%3Cp%3EKCNA%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20most%20recent%20effort%20to%20retrieve%20more%20aid%20from%20North%20Korea%20was%20back%20in%20late%20July%2C%20when%20Russian%20Defense%20Minister%20Sergei%20Shoigu%20%3Ca%