rnment%20money%20to%20private%20entities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20videos%20of%20celebrations%20by%20YSRCP%20leaders%20and%20cadre%2C%20even%20though%20they%20were%20reportedly%20told%20not%20to%20celebrate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20image%20of%20a%2073-year-old%20politician%2C%20widely%20respected%20by%20the%20people%2C%20being%20sent%20to%20jail%20could%20evoke%20sympathy.%20That%20is%20a%20chance%20the%20YSRCP%20would%20not%20want%20to%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20say%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20sympathy%20for%20Mr%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20point%20out%20that%20when%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20advanced%20elections%20in%202004%20following%20a%20Maoist%20attack%20on%20his%20life%2C%20hoping%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20sympathy%2C%20he%20had%20lost%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20YS%20Rajasekhar%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelugu%20Desam%20leaders%20and%20cadre%20appear%20stunned%20and%20yet%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20fight%20this%20onslaught.%20There%20were%20audio%20leaks%20of%20TDP%20leaders%20asking%20its%20cadre%20to%20come%20out%20and%20show%20their%20frustration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20YSRCP%20government%20has%20managed%20to%20stop%20the%20protests%20from%20turning%20violent%20and%20taking%20over%20headlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20elections%20just%20months%20away%2C%20the%20YSRCP%20versus%20TDP%20battle%20will%20be%20fought%20as%20much%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20than%20inside%20courts%20--%20because%20public%20perception%20matters%20more%20in%20the%20theatre%20of%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20if%20Mr%20Naidu%20and%20his%20team%20are%20busy%20playing%20defence%2C%20trying%20to%20stay%20out%20of%20jail%20and%20trouble%2C%20putting%20up%20a%20full-fledged%20fight%20for%20victory%20in%20elections%20could%20become%20a%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitics%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20is%20personal%2C%20vicious%20and%20nasty.%20It%20is%20a%20battle%20where%20punching%20straight%20and%20punching%20below%20the%20belt%20are%20practised%20routinely%20for%20political%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20while%20the%20technicalities%20are%20argued%20in%20court%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20free-for-all%20outside%2C%20with%20YSRCP%20calling%20the%20TDP%20names%20and%20the%20TDP%20accusing%20the%20YSRCP%20of%20playing%20dirty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20YSRCP%20and%20the%20TDP%20have%20their%20loyal%20following%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20so%20at%20political%20rallies%2C%20very%20often%2C%20there%20are%20clashes%20when%20the%20two%20come%20face-to-face.%20That%20is%20only%20likely%20to%20get%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20has%20spent%20five%20years%20out%20of%20power%20and%20for%20a%20regional%20party%2C%20that%20makes%20matters%20tough.%20Mr%20Naidu's%20Telugu%20Desam%20was%20once%20a%20party%20with%20deep%20pockets%2C%20with%20many%20businessmen-turned-politicians%20providing%20it%20with%20the%20fuel%20to%20fight%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20many%20of%20those%20friends%20in%20business%20parted%20ways%20with%20him%20as%20criminal%20cases%20filed%20by%20multiple%20Central%20agencies%20put%20their%20primary%20business%20interest%20in%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20made%20a%20costly%20mistake%20in%202018-19%2C%20when%20he%20split%20ways%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20took%20on%20its%20leadership%2C%20demanding%20special%20category%20status%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Many%20see%20it%20as%20a%20trap%20set%20for%20him%20by%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20who%20had%20played%20his%20cards%20carefully%20and%20cleverly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Naidu%20has%20realised%20that%20it%20does%20not%20pay%20to%20have%20powerful%20enemies%20and%20tried%20multiple%20times%20to%20extend%20a%20hand%20of%20friendship%20again%20towards%20the%20NDA.%20But%20the%20BJP%20was%20apparently%20not%20willing%20to%20forgive%20and%20forget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mr%20Naidu%2C%20walking%20away%20from%20the%20tag%20of%20Remand%20Prisoner%20number%207691%20at%20Rajamahendravam%20Central%20Jail%20is%20going%20to%20be%20tough%20because%20while%20the%20legal%20battle%20is%20fought%2C%20his%20political%20opponents%20will%20throw%20it%20at%20him%20at%20every%20possible%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYSRCP%20leaders%20are%20talking%20about%20how%20this%20is%20only%20the%20beginning.%20There%20is%20much%20more%20to%20come%20and%20not%20for%20Naidu%20alone.%20His%20son%20Nara%20Lokesh%20will%20be%20arrested%20soon%2C%20said%20state%20tourism%20minister%20Roja.%20The%20state%20CID%20chief%20had%20also%20hinted%20at%20questioning%20the%20former%20IT%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20there%20were%20reports%20that%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20had%20received%20notice%20from%20the%20Income%20Tax%20department%20that%20he%20had%20not%20disclosed%20Rs%20118%20crore%20income%20that%20he%20allegedly%20got%20as%20kickback%20from%20top%20infra%20firms%20Shapoorji%20Pallonji%20and%20L%26amp%3BT.%20The%20firms%20were%20awarded%20contracts%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20in%20Amaravati%20when%20he%20was%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20is%20going%20to%20make%20it%20tough-pedalling%20for%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%20Given%20his%20age%20and%20a%20dearth%20of%20second%20rung%20leaders%2C%20it%20will%20be%20an%20uphill%20task%20for%20the%20bicycle.%20A%20puncture%20is%20all%20it%20takes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Uma%20Sudhir%20is%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20NDTV)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694456280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-10%2Fciq3ma1_chandrababu-naidu-twitter_625x300_12_October_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Ffor-chandrababu-naidus-bicycle-a-puncture-is-all-it-takes-4381259%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%