r-paul-pogba-provisionally-suspended-after-testing-positive-for-testosterone-12959353%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Manchester%20United%20midfielder%20Paul%20Pogba%20has%20been%20provisionally%20suspended%20after%20testing%20positive%20for%20a%20banned%20substance%20in%20Italy%2C%20the%20country's%20anti-doping%20agency%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A546%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjuventus-star-paul-pogba-provisionally-suspended-after-testing-positive-for-testosterone-12959353%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjuventus-star-paul-pogba-provisionally-suspended-after-testing-positive-for-testosterone-12959353%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjuventus-star-paul-pogba-provisionally-suspended-after-testing-positive-for-testosterone-12959353%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20Agree%20to%20'Accelerate'%20%2450%20Billion%20West%20Coast%20Refinery%20Project%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11230929%2FF5u9Jfqa8AAj2Mz.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20agreed%20to%20accelerate%20the%20joint%20project%20of%20the%20West%20Coast%20oil%20refinery%2C%20even%20as%20they%20also%20talked%20about%20strengthening%20security%20cooperation%20to%20combat%20terrorism%20during%20discussions%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20Bin%20Salman%20Bin%20Abdulaziz%20Al-Saud%20on%20Monday%2C%20September%2011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20chaired%20the%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20Strategic%20Partnership%20Council%20during%20the%20one-day%20state%20visit%20by%20the%20Saudi%20royal%2C%20who%20stayed%20on%20following%20the%20end%20of%20the%20G20%20summit%20a%20day%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20Modi%20described%20Saudi%20Arabia%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20strategic%20partners.%20Last%20Saturday%2C%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20were%20joined%20by%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20in%20launching%20an%20ambitious%20plane%20for%20an%20economic%20corridor%20linking%20Indian%20ports%20through%20shipping%20and%20rail%20links%20to%20Europe%20via%20the%20Gulf%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20press%20briefing%20following%20the%20talks%2C%20MEA%20secretary%20(CPV)%20Ausaf%20Sayeed%20said%20leaders%20were%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20early%20implementation%20of%20the%20West%20Coast%20refinery%20project%20for%20which%20funds%20worth%20%2450%20billion%20have%20been%20allotted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20set%20up%20a%20joint%20task%20force%20to%20help%20in%20identifying%20and%20channelising%20the%20USD%20100%20billion%20investments%20which%20was%20promised%20by%20the%20Saudi%20side%20half%20of%20which%20was%20for%20the%20refinery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F37110%2FJoint_Statement_during_the_State_Visit_of_HRH_the_Crown_Prince_and_Prime_Minister_of_the_Kingdom_of_Saudi_Arabia_to_India%5C%22%3EThe%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20after%20the%20talks%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20sides%20agreed%20to%20develop%20joint%20projects%20to%20transform%20oil%20into%20petrochemicals%20in%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20and%20providing%20the%20necessary%20support%2C%20requirements%20and%20enablers%20to%20accelerate%20the%20project%20of%20West%20Coast%20Refinery%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20sides%20agreed%20to%20explore%20investment%20opportunities%20in%20the%20field%20of%20fertilisers%20and%20intermediate%2C%20transformative%20and%20specialised%20petrochemicals%20in%20both%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20eight%20pacts%20were%20inked%20for%20cooperation%20in%20a%20range%20of%20areas%20including%20investment%2C%20digitisation%2C%20and%20saltwater%20desalinisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra-based%20West%20Coast%20refinery%20project%2C%20initially%20unveiled%20in%202015%2C%20is%20a%20joint%20project%20between%20ARAMCO%2C%20ADNOC%2C%20and%20Indian%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20countries%20also%20agreed%20to%20establish%20a%20monitoring%20committee%20for%20tracking%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20refinery%20project%2C%20as%20per%20the%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20area%20of%20defence%20sector%2C%20India%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20on%20continuing%20to%20consider%20possibilities%20of%20joint%20development%20and%20production%20of%20defence%20equipment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20announced%20that%20they%20agreed%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimportance%20of%20cooperation%20to%20promote%20ways%20to%20ensure%20the%20security%20and%20safety%20of%20waterways%20and%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20in%20line%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Convention%20on%20the%20Law%20of%20the%20Sea%20(UNCLOS)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20underlined%20the%20need%20to%20strengthen%20security%20cooperation%20in%20combating%20terrorism%20and%20its%20financing.%20%E2%80%9CBoth%20sides%20emphasised%20that%20terrorism%2C%20in%20all%20its%20forms%2C%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20gravest%20threats%20to%20humanity.%20They%20agreed%20that%20there%20cannot%20be%20any%20justification%20for%20any%20act%20of%20terror%20for%20any%20reason%20whatsoever.%20They%20rejected%20any%20attempt%20to%20link%20terrorism%20to%20any%20particular%20race%2C%20religion%20or%20culture.%20Both%20sides%20called%20on%20all%20States%20to%20reject%20the%20use%20of%20terrorism%20against%20other%20countries%2C%20dismantle%20terrorism%20infrastructure%20where%20it%20exists%20and%20bring%20perpetrators%20of%20terrorism%20to%20justice%20swiftly%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20document%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20need%20to%20%E2%80%9Cprevent%20access%20to%20weapons%20including%20missiles%20and%20drones%20to%20commit%20terrorist%20acts%20against%20other%20countries%E2%80%9D.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20been%20targeted%20by%20frequent%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks%20by%20Yemen%E2%80%99s%20Iran-backed%20Houthis%20after%20the%20Saudi-led%20military%20coalition%20intervened%20to%20remove%20the%20Yemeni%20government%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20opening%20remarks%2C%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20recognised%20the%20substantial%20impact%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20residing%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20comprising%207%25%20of%20the%20Saudi%20population.%20He%20reiterated%20that%20Saudi%20Arabia%20considers%20them%20an%20integral%20component%20of%20the%20nation.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20consider%20them%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia.%20We%20watch%20and%20take%20care%20of%20them%20like%20we%20take%20care%20of%20our%20own%20citizens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694454250000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11230929%2FF5u9Jfqa8AAj2Mz.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-saudi-arabia-agree-to-accelerate-50-billion-west-coast-refinery-project%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20a%20discussion%20with%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20Bin%20Salman%20Bin%20Abdulaziz%20Al-Saud%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20described%20Saudi%20Arabia%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20important%20strategic%20partners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-saudi-arabia-agree-to-accelerate-50-billion-west-coast-refinery-project%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SpiceJet%20To%20Pay%20%241.5%20Million%20To%20Credit%20Suisse%20After%20Supreme%20Court%20Order%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESpiceJet%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20would%20pay%20%241.5%20million%20to%20Credit%20Suisse%20as%20demanded%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20SpiceJet%20to%20make%20the%20payment%20by%20September%2015%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20unpaid%20dues%20and%20warned%20the%20budget%20airline%20of%20unspecified%20%26quot%3Bdrastic%20action%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20next%20hearing%20if%20it%20failed%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20of%20the%20amount%20is%20part%20of%20a%20monthly%20settlement%20plan%20SpiceJet%20had%20previously%20agreed%20with%20Credit%20Suisse%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20are%20unpaid%20dues%20to%20the%20bank%20that%20have%20accrued%20since%20last%20year%20after%20the%20airline%20failed%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20payment%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20SpiceJet%20fails%20to%20pay%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20take%20%26quot%3Bdrastic%20action%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20September%2022%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEnough%20of%20this%20dilly-dally%20business%20...%20We%20are%20not%20bothered%20even%20if%20you%20die%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20two%20judges%20said%20during%20the%20hearing%2C%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20SpiceJet%20chief%20Ajay%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20had%20previously%20said%20the%20Credit%20Suisse%20debt%20was%20an%20old%20one%20that%20predated%20the%20tenure%20of%20its%20current%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECredit%20Suisse%20and%20SpiceJet%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20legal%20dispute%20since%202015%20over%20the%20bank's%20claim%20of%20unpaid%20dues%20of%20around%20%2424%20million%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court's%20order%20that%20the%20airline%20be%20wound%20up%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20agreeing%20to%20a%20settlement%20plan%2C%20the%20dues%20were%20not%20paid%2C%20and%20in%20March%20Credit%20Suisse%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20seeking%20to%20initiate%20contempt%20proceedings%20against%20SpiceJet%20and%20Singh%20over%20%26quot%3Ba%20wilful%20and%20intentional%20disobedience%26quot%3B%20of%20court%20orders%20and%20failure%20to%20pay%20dues%20of%20%244.5%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20order%20is%20the%20latest%20setback%20for%20cash-strapped%20SpiceJet%20which%20told%20a%20court%20last%20month%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bstruggling%20to%20stay%20afloat%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20was%20ordered%20to%20pay%20Rs%20100%20crores%20to%20its%20former%20owner%2C%20Kalanithi%20Maran%2C%20by%20September%2010%20as%20part%20of%20an%20arbitration%20order%20in%20a%20separate%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20case%2C%20also%20heard%20on%20Monday%20at%20a%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20SpiceJet%20said%20it%20had%20deposited%20625%20million%20rupees%20of%20that%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20airline%20said%20late%20on%20Monday%20it%20would%20complete%20the%20payment%20of%201%20billion%20rupees%20to%20Mr%20Maran%20by%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694454060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F41t8imeo_spicejet-reuters_625x300_11_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fspicejet-to-pay-1-5-million-to-credit-suisse-after-supreme-court-order-warned-drastic-action-ajay-singh-4381141%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SpiceJet%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%20would%20pay%20%241.5%20million%20to%20Credit%20Suisse%20as%20demanded%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fspicejet-to-pay-1-5-million-to-credit-suisse-after-supreme-court-order-warned-drastic-ac