o%20board%20the%20flight%2C%20had%20been%20informed%20about%20the%20technical%20snag.%20They%20were%20then%20asked%20to%20return%20to%20their%20hotels.%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%2C%20who%20was%20accompanied%20by%20his%20son%20Xavier%2C%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20arrived%20at%20the%20airport%20by%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694452959000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fcanadian-armed-forces-plane-on-its-way-to-pick-up-trudeau-team-stranded-in-delhi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20Canadian%20PMO%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%20and%20his%20team%20may%20fly%20out%20of%20Delhi%20by%20Tuesday%20afternoon%20Indian%20time.%20A%20technical%20snag%20had%20grounded%20the%20aircraft%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20carry%20the%20Canadian%20delegation%20out%20of%20Delhi%2C%20after%20attending%20the%20G20%20Summit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNehru%20Gave%20Away%20UN%20Security%20Council%20Seat%20To%20China%20On%20Platter%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20Monday%20attacked%20the%20Congress%2C%20alleging%20that%20former%20prime%20minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20had%20%26quot%3Bgiven%20away%26quot%3B%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council's%20permanent%20seat%20to%20China%20%26quot%3Bon%20a%20platter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20a%20renewed%20push%20for%20expansion%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC)%20and%20reforms%20in%20all%20global%20institutions%20to%20reflect%20the%20world's%20%26quot%3Bnew%20realities%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20the%20G20%20Summit%20drew%20to%20a%20close%20with%20the%20US%2C%20Russia%20and%20France%20praising%20the%20meeting's%20outcomes%20under%20Indian%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20while%20India%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Modi%20is%20shaping%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20world%20is%20backing%20the%20country's%20bid%20for%20a%20permanent%20UNSC%20seat%2C%20which%20Nehru%20gave%20away%20to%20China%20on%20a%20platter...The%20unpatriotic%20deeds%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20haunt%20our%20history%2C%20to%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20while%20India%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20PM%20Modi%20is%20shaping%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20world%20is%20backing%20the%20country's%20bid%20for%20a%20permanent%20UNSC%20seat%2C%20which%20Nehru%20gave%20away%20to%20China%20on%20a%20platter%E2%80%A6%20The%20unpatriotic%20deeds%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20haunt%20our%20history%2C%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20BJP%20(%40BJP4India)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBJP4India%2Fstatus%2F1701187942084128926%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2011%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UNSC%20has%20five%20permanent%20members%20--%20the%20US%2C%20China%2C%20France%2C%20Britain%20and%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20fresh%20pitch%20for%20expansion%20of%20the%20UNSC%20and%20reforms%20in%20global%20institutions%2C%20Modi%20had%20also%20said%20that%20in%20order%20to%20take%20the%20world%20towards%20a%20better%20future%2C%20it%20is%20necessary%20that%20the%20global%20systems%20are%20according%20to%20the%20present%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20is%20also%20an%20example%20of%20this.%20When%20the%20UN%20was%20established%2C%20the%20world%20was%20completely%20different%20from%20what%20it%20is%20today.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20there%20were%2051%20founding%20members%20in%20the%20UN.%20Today%20the%20number%20of%20countries%20included%20in%20the%20UN%20is%20around%20200%2C%26quot%3B%20Modi%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20this%2C%20the%20number%20of%20permanent%20members%20in%20the%20UNSC%20remains%20the%20same.%20The%20world%20has%20since%20changed%20a%20lot%20in%20every%20aspect.%20Be%20it%20transport%2C%20communication%2C%20health%20and%20education%2C%20every%20sector%20has%20been%20transformed.%20These%20new%20realities%20should%20reflect%20in%20our%20new%20global%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20renewed%20push%20for%20expansion%20of%20the%20UNSC%2C%20Brazilian%20President%20Luiz%20Inacio%20Lula%20da%20Silva%20on%20Monday%20echoed%20similar%20views%20and%20called%20for%20reform%20of%20the%20powerful%20UN%20body%20to%20reflect%20contemporary%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil%20is%20the%20next%20chair%20of%20the%20G20%20bloc.%20The%20president%20also%20said%20that%20his%20country%20wants%20the%20equality%20issue%20to%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bcore%20issue%26quot%3B%20during%20its%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20Turkish%20President%20Recep%20Tayyip%20Erdogan%20said%20Turkiye%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bproud%26quot%3B%20if%20a%20country%20like%20India%20becomes%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20(UNSC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Erdogan%20had%20said%20all%20non-P5%20members%20should%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20become%20members%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%20by%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20US%20President%20Biden%20had%20lauded%20India's%20G20%20Presidency%20for%20further%20%26quot%3Bdemonstrating%26quot%3B%20how%20the%20G20%20as%20a%20forum%20is%20delivering%20important%20outcomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContinuing%20to%20share%20the%20view%20that%20global%20governance%20must%20be%20more%20inclusive%20and%20representative%2C%20President%20Biden%20reaffirmed%20his%20support%20for%20a%20reformed%20UNSC%20with%20Ind