g%20important%20was%20lacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20describe%20the%20feeling%20it%20gives%20you.%20It%20reminded%20me%20of%20when%20other%20cultures%20say%2C%20'Don't%20take%20my%20picture%20because%20it%20is%20taking%20away%20your%20soul%2C%26quot%3B%20Burton%20told%20The%20Independent%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20does%20is%20it%20sucks%20something%20from%20you.%20It%20takes%20something%20from%20your%20soul%20or%20psyche%3B%20that%20is%20very%20disturbing%2C%20especially%20if%20it%20has%20to%20do%20with%20you.%20It's%20like%20a%20robot%20taking%20your%20humanity%2C%20your%20soul.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222106%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20from%20Buzzfeed%20article%20of%20Tim%20Burton%20style%20Disney%20characters%20include%20an%20image%20of%20Elsa%20in%20a%20foggy%2C%20dark%20graveyard%20wearing%20dark%20makeup%2C%20curly%20hair%20and%20a%20black%20dress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ff273ba39a1b00190d1af9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221579%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20BuzzFeed%20article%20features%20dark%20and%20creepy%20versions%20of%20Disney%20characters%2C%20like%20Elsa%20from%20Frozen.%3Cp%3EBuzzfeed%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuzzFeed's%20article%2C%20which%20is%20well%20worth%20a%20look%2C%20used%20the%20AI%20art-generation%20tool%20Midjourney%20to%20create%20images%20of%20Disney%20characters%20in%20Tim%20Burton's%20charming%20but%20creepy%20art%20style%2C%20applying%20the%20treatment%20to%20characters%20in%20popular%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BFrozen%26quot%3B%20(pictured%20above)%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Little%20Mermaid%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BPrincess%20and%20the%20Frog%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBeauty%20and%20the%20Beast.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurton's%20remarks%20add%20to%20the%20growing%20conversation%20and%20debate%20on%20AI%20artwork%2C%20which%20burst%20onto%20the%20scene%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20as%20AI%20