own%20into%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Bikaner%20Sunday%2C%20Mr%20Shekhawat%20said%20Rajasthan%20is%20indeed%20a%20%26quot%3Bstate%20of%20men%26quot%3B%20and%20its%20%E2%80%9Cmasculinity%E2%80%9D%20kept%20Hinduism%20and%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20alive.%20But%20he%20described%20Mr%20Dhariwal's%20comment%20as%20a%20blot%20on%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmasculinity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhariwal%2C%20who%20is%20the%20state's%20urban%20development%20and%20housing%20minister%2C%20had%20triggered%20a%20row%20in%20March%202022%20when%20appeared%20to%20justify%20rapes%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BRajasthan%20mardon%20ka%20Pradesh%20hai.%26quot%3B%20Targeting%20him%2C%20Mr%20Shekhawat%20said%20that%20when%20Dhariwal%20insulted%20Rajasthan%20through%20his%20comments%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20Congress%20MLAs%20laughed%20and%20clapped%20like%20%26quot%3Bimpotent%20men%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Beunuchs%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20BJP%20has%20been%20mounting%20attack%20on%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20over%20the%20minister's%20remark%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20due%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shekhawat%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BRajasthan%20was%20insulted%20on%20the%20day%20when%20Shanti%20Dhariwal%20said%20that%20more%20rapes%20happen%20in%20Rajasthan%20because%20Rajasthan%20is%20a%20state%20of%20men.%20Behind%20him%2C%20Congress%20MLAs%20were%20laughing%20and%20clapping%20like%20impotent%20men%20and%20eunuchs%20when%20he%20made%20the%20statement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainly%20Rajasthan%20is%20a%20state%20of%20men.%20Because%20of%20the%20masculinity%20of%20Rajasthan%2C%20Hinduism%20and%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20are%20alive%20in%20India%20today.%20If%20Prithviraj%20Chauhan%2C%20Bappa%20Rawal%2C%20Rana%20Sanga%2C%20Veer%20Durgadas%2C%20Rao%20Chandra%20Sen%2C%20Maharana%20Pratap%20had%20not%20been%2