ke-race-against-time-to-reach-survivors-as-number-killed-nears-2-700-12959250%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmorocco-earthquake-race-against-time-to-reach-survivors-as-number-killed-nears-2-700-12959250%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Delhi%20Declaration%20Sent%20A%20%26quot%3BPositive%20Signal%26quot%3B%3A%20China%20In%20First%20Comments%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina%20finally%20broke%20its%20silence%20on%20the%20New%20Delhi%20G20%20summit%20saying%20that%20the%20Declaration%20adopted%20by%20the%20member%20nations%20has%20sent%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpositive%20signal%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20influential%20grouping%20is%20%E2%80%9Cworking%20together%E2%80%9D%20to%20tackle%20global%20challenges%20and%20promote%20world%20economic%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20on%20Saturday%20pulled%20off%20a%20big%20diplomatic%20win%20after%20the%20G20%20summit%20held%20under%20its%20presidency%20adopted%20a%20consensus%20declaration%20overcoming%20major%20differences%20on%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20called%20for%20ending%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20trust%20deficit%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20comment%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20two-day%20summit%2C%20which%20concluded%20Sunday%2C%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spoke%20highly%20of%20its%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20summit%20adopted%20a%20leaders'%20declaration%2C%20which%20reflects%20China's%20proposition%20and%20states%20that%20the%20G20%20would%20act%20in%20concrete%20ways%20through%20partnerships%2C%20sending%20a%20positive%20signal%20of%20the%20G20%20working%20together%20to%20tackle%20global%20challenges%20and%20promote%20world%20economic%20recovery%20and%20global%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20for%20her%20comment%20on%20the%20summit%20outcome%2C%20Mao%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20process%20of%20preparing%20for%20this%20New%20Delhi%20summit%2C%20China%20played%20a%20constructive%20role%20and%20always%20supported%20the%20summit%20in%20attaching%20importance%20to%20the%20concerns%20of%20developing%20countries%20and%20reaching%20fruitful%20outcomes%20in%20support%20of%20common%20development.%E2%80%9D%20Chinese%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20attended%20the%20summit%2C%20deputising%20for%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20China%20supports%20the%20absence%20of%20direct%20criticism%20of%20Russia%20in%20the%20G20%20statement%20and%20whether%20softer%20language%20would%20help%20end%20the%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Mao%20said%20China's%20stance%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20issue%20is%20consistent%20and%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20G20%20leaders'%20declaration%20is%20the%20result%20of%20consensus%20reached%20through%20consultation%20and%20reflects%20the%20common%20understanding%20of%20all%20members.%20The%20New%20Delhi%20Summit%20reaffirms%20that%20the%20G20%20is%20the%20premier%20forum%20for%20international%20economic%20cooperation%2C%20not%20a%20platform%20to%20resolve%20geopolitical%20and%20security%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20believe%20that%20the%20key%20to%20the%20final%20resolution%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20crisis%20lies%20in%20discarding%20the%20Cold%20War%20mentality%2C%20attaching%20importance%20to%20and%20respecting%20all%20sides'%20legitimate%20security%20concerns%2C%20and%20seeking%20a%20political%20solution%20through%20dialogue%20and%20negotiation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20said%20China%20will%20remain%20committed%20to%20promoting%20peace%20talks%20and%20working%20together%20with%20the%20international%20community%20for%20the%20political%20settlement%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMao%20said%20China%20has%20always%20attached%20importance%20to%20and%20actively%20supported%20the%20work%20of%20the%20G20%20and%20believes%20that%20it's%20important%20for%20the%20grouping%20to%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20and%20cooperate%20to%20address%20various%20risks%20and%20challenges%20in%20the%20world%20economy%20and%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20his%20attendance%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Premier%20Li%20Qiang%20elaborated%20on%20China's%20views%20and%20propositions%20on%20G20%20cooperation%2C%20calling%20on%20all%20parties%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20original%20aspiration%20of%20solidarity%20and%20cooperation%2C%20live%20up%20to%20the%20responsibility%20for%20peace%20and%20development%20as%20required%20by%20our%20times%2C%20and%20be%20partners%20in%20promoting%20the%20world%20economic%20recovery%2C%20open%20cooperation%20and%20global%20sustainable%20development%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20member%20countries%20represent%20around%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20global%20GDP%2C%20over%2075%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20global%20trade%2C%20and%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20world%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grouping%20comprises%20Argentina%2C%20Australia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Canada%2C%20China%2C%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20India%2C%20Indonesia%2C%20Italy%2C%20Japan%2C%20the%20Republic%20of%20Korea%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Russia%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20South%20Africa%2C%20Turkey%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20the%20African%20Union%20was%20admitted%20as%20G20's%20permanent%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694444160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fbt3g7rs4_china-pm-g20-1200_625x300_11_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fg20-delhi-declaration-sent-a-positive-signal-china-in-first-comments-4380429%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20finally%