Sachin%20Pilot%20also%20targeted%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20saying%20it%20only%20misleads%20people%20and%20talks%20about%20religion%20to%20come%20into%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20BJP%20leaders%20questioning%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20who%20held%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20Niwai%2C%20Tonk%20on%20Sunday%2C%20for%20not%20visiting%20Rajasthan%20after%20incidents%20of%20crime%20against%20women%2C%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%20the%20opposition%20party%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20law%20and%20order%20an%20issue%20as%20assembly%20elections%20are%20approaching%20in%20Rajasthan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20any%20incident%20has%20taken%20place%2C%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20and%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested%20within%20hours.%20Such%20incidents%20can%20happen%20anywhere%20but%20we%20have%20taken%20immediate%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20Sachin%20Pilot%20told%20reporters%20in%20Dausa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20our%20best%20to%20curb%20such%20incidents.%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20other%20states%20also%20has%20to%20be%20seen.%20The%20graph%20of%20crime%20is%20high%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20are%20making%20an%20issue%20here%20as%20Assembly%20elections%20are%20coming%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Tonk%20MLA%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20Pilot%20said%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20are%20raising%20a%20hue%20and%20cry%20over%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Rajasthan%20were%20not%20visible%20for%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Now%20they%20have%20started%20misleading%20people%20as%20elections%20are%20due%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20also%20said%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20should%20have%20been%20invited%20to%20the%20G20%20gala%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Mr%20Kharge%20was%20invited%2C%20the%20world%20would%20have%20seen%20that%20the%20country%20is%20united%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20hosted%20the%20G20%20dinner%20on%20Saturday%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20venue%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20of%20world%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20addressing%20a%20Kisan%20Sammelan%20in%20Bandikui%2C%20Sachin%20Pilot%20said%20that%20the%20youth%20need%20to%20understand%20the%20thinking%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20mislead%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInflation%20is%20rising%2C%20industries%20are%20getting%20shut.%20Airports%2C%20railways%2C%20powerhouses%20were%20sold%20at%20throw-away%20prices.%20But%2C%20the%20Centre%20is%20busy%20creating%20an%20issue%20over%20the%20country's%20name.%20Both%20India%20and%20Bharat%20pre-exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20invention%20have%20you%20done%3F%20Youths%20need%20to%20understand%20this%20thinking%20to%20mislead%20them.%20If%20we%20are%20lacking%20then%20tell%20us%2C%20but%20first%20understand%20them%20who%20are%20looting%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pilot%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20(BJP)%20have%20only%20one%20work%20that%20is%20to%20mislead%20and%20incite%20people%2C%20talk%20about%20religion%20and%20caste%20to%20get%20into%20power%20and%20chant%20Ram-Ram.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pilot%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%20has%20not%20brought%20any%20policy%20in%20its%20nine%20years%20of%20rule%20and%20only%20gave%20speeches%20and%20published%20advertisements.%20He%20said%20that%20while%20the%20UPA%20government%20brought%20MGNREGA%20and%20RTE%2C%20and%20waived-off%20loans%20of%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20NDA%20government%20implemented%20demonetisation%20and%20faulty%20GST%2C%20increased%20the%20price%20of%20LPG%20cylinder%20manifold%2C%20and%20brought%20Agniveer%20scheme%20for%20defence%20forces%20enthusiasts%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20Pilot%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%20had%20promised%20to%20bring%20back%20black%20money%20in%20the%20country%20and%2