or%20airplanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Brazil%20has%20flown%20a%20plane%20on%20100%20per%20cent%20ethanol%2C%20In%20India%2C%20a%20Pune-Delhi%20Air%20Asia%20flight%20has%20been%20run%20with%20one%20per%20cent%20ethanol%2C%20Mr%20Puri%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20calculated%20that%20if%20we%20have%20to%20make%20one%20percent%20sustainable%20aviation%20fuel%20mandatory%2C%20then%20we%20would%20need%204%20crore%20litres%20that%20would%20benefit%205%2C00%2C000%20of%20our%20farmers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694440980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F9gfq69ac_hardeep-puri_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiofuel-in-indias-cars-and-planes-hardeep-puri-explains-4380441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bio-fuel%20mixes%20are%20being%20across%20the%20world%20and%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20a%20Japanese%20or%20German%20car%20running%20in%20Brazil%20will%20not%20run%20in%20India%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Puri%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiofuel-in-indias-cars-and-planes-hardeep-puri-explains-4380441%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiofuel-in-indias-cars-and-planes-hardeep-puri-explains-4380441%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbiofuel-in-indias-cars-and-planes-hardeep-puri-explains-4380441%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22To%20Superstar%20Rajinikanth%2C%20A%20Gratitude%20Note%20From%20Jailer%20Director%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frajinikanth-s-jailer-collects-over-rs-500-crore-worldwide-4315792%5C%22%3ERajnikanth's%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20been%20making%20all%20the%20right%20noises.%20The%20film%2C%20which%20marked%20the%20superstar's%20return%20to%20the%20big%20screens%20after%20two%20years%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjailer-producers-swanky-gift-to-rajinikanth-on-the-films-success-4350636%5C%22%3Ecollected%20more%20than%20Rs%20600%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20box%20office%20(worldwide).%20The%20film%20was%20released%20on%20August%2010.%20Now%2C%20director%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar%20has%20expressed%20his%20gratitude%20towards%20Rajnikanth%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20crew.%20Nelson%20has%20also%20dropped%20a%20series%20of%20pictures%20on%20Instagram.%20The%20post%20included%20screenshots%20of%20a%20detailed%20letter%2C%20written%20by%C2%A0%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar.%20He%20has%20acknowledged%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer's%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9Chistoric%20success.%E2%80%9D%20The%2039-year-old's%20letter%20read%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20take%20this%20moment%20to%20express%20my%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20and%20sincere%20thanks%20to%20everyone%20for%20making%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20massive%20success.%E2%80%9D%20While%20extending%20his%20support%20to%20all%20the%20distributors%2C%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20start%20by%20thanking%20the%20press%20and%20media%20for%20your%20constant%20love%20and%20support.%20I%20would%20also%20like%20to%20extend%20my%20support%20to%20all%20the%20distributors%20and%20exhibitors%20of%20Jailer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20also%20thanked%20Rajinikanth%20for%20giving%20him%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20opportunity%E2%80%9D%20to%20work%20together.%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar%20added%20that%20Rajinikanth's%20dedication%20and%20energy%20have%20%E2%80%9Calways%20been%20a%20learning%20experience%E2%80%9D%20for%20him%20and%20the%20entire%20crew%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Frajinikanth-is-the-highest-paid-actor-in-india-report-4347713%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSuperstar%20Rajinikanth%20sir%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20thank%20you%20so%20much%20for%20the%20opportunity.%20Your%20energy%2C%20commitment%2C%20dedication%2C%20passion%2C%20simplicity%20and%20humbleness%20have%20always%20been%20a%20learning%20experience%20for%20me%20and%20the%20whole%20crew.%E2%80%9D%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar%20added%20that%20the%20success%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20most%20treasured%20experience%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20life.%20%E2%80%9CYour%20phenomenon%20has%20pushed%20boundaries%2C%20broken%20records%20and%20made%20Jailer%20a%20tremendous%20success.%20I%20shall%20cherish%20this%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20most%20treasured%20experiences%20of%20my%20life%E2%80%9D%2C%20added%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20team%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20indeed%20a%20great%20pleasure%20working%20with%20you%20all.%E2%80%9D%20He%20also%20thanked%20Tamannaah%20Bhatia%2C%20Mohanlal%2C%20Shivarajkumar%2C%20and%20Jackie%20Shroff%20for%20%E2%80%9Celevating%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20their%20presence.%20The%20letter%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CTamannaah%20%5BBhatia%5D%20ji%2C%20I%20feel%20so%20humbled%20by%20your%20magnanimity%20in%20accepting%20the%20role.%20We%20had%20a%20wonderful%20time%20working%20with%20you.%20Mohanlal%20sir%2C%20Shiva%20Rajkumar%20sir%2C%20Jackie%20Shroff%20sir%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20you%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20heart.%20Your%20presence%20has%20elevated%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20greater%20heights.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer's%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0music%20composer%20Anirudh%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Crockstar%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRockstar%20Anirudh%2C%20you%20have%20always%20given%20me%20your%20love%20and%20unwavering%20support.%20Your%20music%20is%20the%20soul%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Thank%20you%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20concluded%20the%20letter%20by%20extending%20his%20heartfelt%20gratitude%20to%20all%20the%20fans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxA2bYuR8RE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxA2bYuR8RE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxA2bYuR8RE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxA2bYuR8RE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Nelson%20Dilipkumar%20(%40nelsondilipkumar)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Rajinikanth's%20crime%20drama%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EJailer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fjailer-ott-release-watch-rajinikanths-film-on-this-date-4350696%5C%22%3Epremiered%20on%20Prim