al%20advantage%2C%20the%20team%20management%20may%20have%20a%20perfect%20solution%20to%20their%20dilemma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20road%20to%20recovery%20for%20KL%20Rahul.%20The%20right-handed%20batter%20showed%20glimpses%20of%20form%20during%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202023%20but%20a%20thigh%20injury%20completely%20ruined%20his%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extent%20of%20the%20injury%20was%20such%20that%20Rahul%20had%20to%20undergo%20surgery%20and%20the%20long%20absence%20only%20fueled%20doubts%20regarding%20his%20return%20to%20the%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20fans%20and%20some%20experts%20were%20not%20convinced%20about%20his%20inclusion%20in%20the%20side%20for%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20and%20ICC%20World%20Cup%202023%20and%20it%20looked%20like%20he%20had%20a%20tough%20journey%20ahead%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20got%20injured%20while%20trying%20to%20chase%20a%20ball%20and%20my%20tendon%20snapped.%20I%20had%20a%20full-fledged%20tear%2C%20my%20tendon%20ripped%20apart%20from%20my%20quadricep.%20So%20when%20it%20happened%2C%20I%20was%20obviously%20me%2C%20my%20family%2C%20the%20franchise%2C%20the%20team%2C%20everybody%20had%20their%20fingers%20crossed%20hoping%20that%20wasn't%20a%20big%20tear%2C%20it%20was%20a%20small%20strain%20or%20I%20could%20get%20better%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalled%20during%20an%20interview%20on%20BCCI.tv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20once%20we%20did%20the%20scans%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20we%20knew%20it%20was%20a%20full%20tear%20and%20it%20was%20quite%20clear%20that%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20I%20can%20get%20better%20from%20this%20injury%20was%20to%20go%20under%20the%20knife%20and%20do%20surgery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20that%20did%20not%20stop%20Rahul%20as%20he%20completed%20his%20recovery%20at%20the%20National%20Cricket%20Academy%20(NCA)%20in%20Bengaluru%20and%20was%20also%20included%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20squad%20as%20a%20wicket-keeper%20batter.%20But%2C%20tragedy%20struck%20once%20again%20as%20a%20niggle%20meant%20that%20he%20missed%20the%20first%20two%20games%20of%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20debate%20surrounding%20Rahul%20or%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ishan%20Kishan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107047-ishan-kishan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EIshan%20Kishan%3C%2Fa%3E%20getting%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20continued%20to%20intensify.%20With%20a%2081-ball-82%20against%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20group%20stages%2C%20Kishan%20made%20a%20solid%20case%20for%20himself%20and%20it%20looked%20like%20Rahul%20may%20not%20find%20a%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20late%20injury%20to%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shreyas%20Iyer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64384-shreyas-santosh-iyer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShreyas%20Iyer%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20as%20a%20somewhat%20bittersweet%20opportunity%20for%20Rahul%20and%20he%20did%20not%20miss%20the%20chance%20to%20somewhat%20silence%20his%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694438400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fvc3bar08_q_625x300_11_September_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Findia-versus-pakistan-asia-cup-2023-kl-rahuls-perfect-comeback-provides-india-with-a-solution-to-no-4-dilemma-4380282%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22KL%20Rahul%20scored%20a%20brilliant%20century%20for%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20during%20the%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20match%20against%20Pakistan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A71%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Findia-versus-pakistan-asia-cup-2023-kl-rahuls-perfect-comeback-provides-india-with-a-solution-to-no-4-dilemma-4380282%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fasia-cup-2023%2Findia-versus-pakista