20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAugust%20and%20September%20are%20critical%20months%20for%20apple%20producers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fhimachal-pradesh-cm-declares-state-a-natural-calamity-affected-area%2Farticle67210401.ece%5C%22%3Edeclared%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20incessant%20rains%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98natural%20calamity%E2%80%99%20as%20torrential%20rains%2C%20floods%20and%20landslides%20killed%20around%20330%20people%2C%20and%20damaged%20over%2012%2C000%20houses.%20The%20state%20has%20suffered%20a%20loss%20of%20over%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrop%20losses%20were%20the%20final%20straw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20new%20government%20these%20only%20indicate%20growing%20challenges%20for%20the%20first%20time%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20challenge%2C%20perhaps%2C%20comes%20from%20the%20horticulture%20farmers%20who%20are%20a%20major%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fhimachal-climate-change-apple-production-prices%5C%22%3EIs%20the%20Changing%20Climate%20Eating%20the%20Apple%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20declining%20apple%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20apple%20harvests%20in%20the%20state%20have%20encountered%20ongoing%20challenges%20throughout%20the%20current%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20on%20a%20closer%20look%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20Himachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20apple%20economy%20is%20decaying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20production%20has%20sharply%20declined%2C%20along%20with%20soil%20fertility.%20Each%20year%20the%20bill%20for%20agri-chemicals%20and%20fertilisers%20is%20doubling%20but%20production%20for%20even%20the%20most%20progressive%20farmers%20is%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarmer%20temperatures%20are%20shifting%20the%20apple%20belt%20to%20higher%20mountain%20plains%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20old%20apple%20growing%20belts%20can%20no%20longer%20grow%20apples.%20They%20are%20forced%20to%20diversify%20by%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20there%20is%20a%20dearth%20of%20infrastructure%20such%20as%20cold%20storages%20and%20mini-processing%20plants%20at%20the%20village%20or%20block%20level.%20This%20increases%20the%20post-harvest%20losses%20for%20apple%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20ever-widening%20gap%20between%20the%20current%20best%20practices%20in%20apple%20farming%20and%20the%20methods%20used%20by%20apple%20growers.%20However%2C%20the%20public%20agriculture%20university%20system%20has%20been%20working%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20have%20been%20using%20excessive%20fertilisers%2C%20pesticides%20and%20fungicides%2C%20which%20have%20contaminated%20the%20soil%20and%20water.%20Therefore%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20the%20damage%20to%20Himachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20biodiversity%20appears%20to%20be%20irreversible.%20This%20situation%20has%20also%20affected%20the%20rural%20communities%20and%20their%20health%2C%20resulting%20in%20increased%20cases%20of%20cancer%20and%20other%20food-style%20diseases%20such%20as%20diabetes%2C%20obesity%2C%20infertility%2C%20etc.%20across%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20apple%20economy%20is%20declining%20due%20to%20agronomic%2C%20changing%20climate%20or%20economic%20reasons%2C%20rural%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20is%20reporting%20higher%20crime%20rate%20and%20drug%20use.%20If%20the%20apple%20economy%20crashes%2C%20it%20will%20have%20a%20grave%20impact%20on%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20rural%20economy.%20Hence%2C%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20take%20corrective%20steps%20to%20rejuvenate%20the%20rural%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fafter-a-record-dry-august-is-indias-kharif-harvest-in-trouble%5C%22%3EAfter%20a%20Record%20Dry%20August%2C%20Is%20India%E2%80%99s%20Kharif%20Harvest%20in%20Trouble%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESolutions%20to%20healing%20the%20apple%20economy%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20one%20should%20be%20concerned%20by%20the%20declining%20apple%20economy%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20path%20to%20recovery%20begins%20with%20farmers.%20To%20gain%20an%20understanding%20on%20their%20concerns%20and%20proposed%20solutions%2C%3Cem%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20some%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20apple%20farmers%20are%20plagued%20with%20many%20issues.%20Because%20of%20growing%20soil%20contamination%2C%20our%20fungicide%20usage%20has%20doubled%2C%20and%20fertiliser%20usage%20is%20also%20increasing%20each%20year.%20However%2C%20production%20has%20been%20declining%2C%20even%20after%20professionally%20using%20the%20prescribed%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Tikkamram%20Thakur%2C%20progressive%20apple%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20our%20farmers%20need%20the%20weather%20predictions%20and%20hail%20and%20rain%20alerts.%20This%20can%20be%20done%20via%20a%20simple%20SMS.%20The%20other%20urgent%20need%20is%20to%20have%20soil%20testing%20labs%20at%20the%20block%20level%2C%20so%20that%20farmers%20can%20get%20their%20soil%20tested%20for%20organic%20matter%20and%20other%20minerals%2C%20too.%20Currently%2C%20many%20farmers%20cannot%20get%20to%20the%20soil%20testing%20labs.%20And%20fungicide%20makers%20should%20be%20made%20responsible%20for%20their%20products.%20The%20state%20agriculture%20university%20should%20have%20to%20prescribe%20the%20fungicide%2Fpesticide%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20so%20that%20there%20is%20no%20overuse%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20the%20agriculture%20university%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20involvement%20of%20extension%20officers%20and%20the%20university%20in%20farmers%E2%80%99%20training.%20We%20need%20to%20made%20aware%20about%20the%20new%20technologies%20and%20varieties%20in%20apples%2C%20so%20that%20we%20can%20remain%20competitive%20in%20the%20market.%20At%20present%2C%20the%20relationship%20between%20horticulture%20officers%20and%20farmers%20is%20broken.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20build%20on%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20big%20challenge%20is%20the%20post-harvest%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuder%20Chand%2C%2045%2C%20an%20apple%20farmer%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20to%20have%20mini%20cold%20storage%20or%20a%20large%20public-private-owned%20cold%20storage%20at%20the%20block%20level.%20And%20the%20districts%20or%20blocks%20that%20cannot%20have%20cold%20storage%20should%20be%20supplied%20with%20mini%20processing%20plants.%20We%20can%20make%20chips%20to%20wine%20from%20apples.%20With%20the%20right%20incentives%20and%20policy%20changes%2C%20the%20government%20can%20turn%20the%20apple%20economy%20around%20and%20reduce%20post-harvest%20losses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYograj%20Thakur%2C%2041%2C%20an%20apple%20farmer%20with%20five%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20need%20for%20diversification%20in%20the%20area.%20Otherwise%20climate%20change%20and%20supply%20and%20demand%20challenges%20can%20never%20be%20met.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20harvest%20Himachal%20is%20flooded%20with%20apples%2C%20which%20causes%20the%20prices%20to%20crash.%20As%20there%20are%20no%20cold%20storages%20available%20at%20the%20village%20levels%2C%20farmers%20have%20to%20sell%20their%20apples%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20If%20we%20diversify%20into%20plum%2C%20kiwi%20or%20even%20think%20of%20organic%20farming%20we%20could%20produce%20fruits%2C%20vegetables%20in%20other%20months%2C%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20various%20discussions%20this%20author%20had%20with%20farmers%2C%20one%20innovative%20idea%20emerged%3A%20to%20explore%20agro-tourism%20and%20establish%20partnerships%20with%20hotels%20and%20Airbnb%20accommodations%20in%20popular%20tourist%20destinations%20like%20Manali.%20These%20partnerships%20could%20involve%20providing%20guests%20with%20cartons%20of%20apples%20alongside%20their%20room%20bookings.%20The%20associated%20costs%20could%20be%20incorporated%20into%20the%20room%20rates%2C%20especially%20for%20mid%20and%20upper-range%20hotels.%20This%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%20tax%E2%80%9D%20directly%20contributing%20to%20the%20revival%20and%20support%20of%20the%20local%20apple%20economy%2C%20considering%20the%20millions%20of%20people%20who%20visit%20Manali%20and%20other%20Himachali%20tourist%20spots%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20believed%20that%20if%20this%20initiative%20is%20successfully%20implemented%2C%20a%20substantial%20portion%20of%20Himachal%E2%80%99s%20apple%20production%20could%20be%20consumed%20within%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20is%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20was%20the%20former%20director%20of%20policy%20and%20outreach%20at%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Eagri-talk%20show%20%E2%80%98Krishi%20ki%20baat%E2%80%99%20(Farm%20Talks).%20He%20tweets%20%40indrassingh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694437234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F02153447%2FApple_tree_loaded.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fsoil-testing-labs-more-cold-storages-farmers-propose-ways-to-heal-himachal-pradeshs-apple-economy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Himachal%20Pradesh's%20apple%20economy%20has%20suffered%20an%20estimated%20loss%20of%20over%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20climate%20change%20that%20has%20badly%20hit%20the%20state's%20apple%20economy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fsoil-testing-labs-more-cold-storages-farmers-propose-ways-to-heal-himachal-pradeshs-apple-economy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Martech%20Tools%20Are%20No%20Panacea%20for%20Marketing%20Ills%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11171020%2Fstephen-dawson-qwtCeJ5cLYs-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIndia%20Inc.%20has%20been%20steadily%20increasing%20its%20investments%20in%20technology%20for%20marketing%2C%20and%20as%20many%20as%2088%25%20of%20surveyed%20enterprises%20confirmed%20boosting%20this%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years.%20However%2C%20the%20average%20allocation%20of%20marketing%20budgets%20to%20ManTech%20is%20only%2015%25%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20global%20average%20of%2026%25.%20Looks%20like%20this%20gap%20will%20be%20closed%20in%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20going%20by%20the%20projections%20of%20match%20providers%20%E2%80%93%20India%20will%20be%20a%20US%24%2040%20billion%20market%20by%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMartech%20tools%20automate%20various%20marketing%20tasks%20such%20as%20email%20campaigns%2C%20social%20media%20scheduling%2C%20and%20lead%20nurturing.%20The%20resultant%20efficiency%20frees%20up%20the%20executive%20time%20for%20strategic%20planning%20and%20creative%20thinking.%20Many%20marketers%20today%20seamlessly%20execute%20multichannel%20marketing%20campaigns%20with%20consistent%20messaging%20across%20various%20platforms.%20While%20they%20have%20undoubtedly%20revolutionised%20the%20field%2C%20can%20they%20serve%20as%20the%20panacea%20for%20all%20marketing%20challenges%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgreed%2C%20ManTech%20has%20delivered%20undeniable%20benefits%20to%20modern%20marketing%20efforts%20in%20several%20ways.%20Data%20analytics%2C%20and%20insights%20thereof%2C%20have%20helped%20marketers%20to%20make%20better%20decisions%20by%20understanding%20consumer%20behaviour%2C%20preferences%2C%20and%20trends.%20It%20has%20also%20helped%20in%20better%20segmentation%20and%20creating%20customised%20experiences%20for%20each%20segment%2C%20resulting%20in%20improved%20conversion%20rates%20and%20customer%20loyalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20it%20always%20has%20worked%20wonders%20for%20companies.%20Take%20for%20instance%20the%20cases%20of%20Snapdeal%2C%20Oyo%2C%20Zomato%2C%20housing.com%2C%20and%20Makemytrip.%20All%20of%20them%20were%20early%20adapters%20of%20Martech%20and%20have%20not%20yet%20found%20the%20required%20results.%20Snapdeal%20ran%20into%20financial%20difficulties%2C%20Zomato%20could%20acquire%20customers%20but%20not%20get%20profitable%20ones%2C%20Oyo%20failed%20to%20deliver%20the%20quality%20hospitality%20their%20customers%20wanted%2C%20Housing.com%20faced%20leadership%20and%20operational%20difficulties%2C%20and%20Makemytrip%20could%20not%20convert%20insights%20into%20personalised%20customer%20experiences%2C%20and%20got%20merged%20with%20Ibibo%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChallenges%20galore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20there%20are%20many%20challenges.%20Many%20organisations%20use%20a%20multitude%20of%20Martech%20tools%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20integration%20issues.%20Disconnected%20systems%20may%20hinder%20seamless%20data%20flow%2C%20resulting%20in%20incomplete%20insights%20and%20disjointed%20customer%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20any%20technology%2C%20unless%20it%20is%20a%20rogue%20AI%20algorithm%2C%20needs%20human%20expertise%20for%20optimal%20utilisation%20of%20its%20features.%20Relying%20solely%20on%20technology%20without%20skilled%20professionals%20can%20lead%20to%20not%20only%20underutilisation%20and%20misinterpretation%20of%20data%20but%20also%20expensive%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20complexity%20of%20some%20Martech%20platforms%20may%20pose%20a%20learning%20curve%20situation%20for%20marketing%20teams%2C%20potentially%20slowing%20down%20the%20implementation%20process%20and%20delaying%20results.%20T