3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20now%20has%202%2C500%20visitors%20a%20day%20and%20the%20team%20insists%20that%20care%20has%20been%20taken%20to%20not%20alienate%20the%20average-everyday%20visitor.%20Nothing%20is%20overtly%20intellectualised%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20costly%20and%20difficult-to-maintain%20technology%20has%20been%20limited%20to%20only%20enhance%20the%20experience%20of%20viewers%20and%20for%20interactive%20interventions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20G20%20exhibition%20had%20an%20immersive%20quality%20to%20it%2C%20and%20this%20immersive%20nature%20extended%20to%20both%20the%20temporary%20exhibitions%20organised%20for%20the%20biennale%20and%20the%20permanent%20museum%20displays.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fundamental%20aim%20of%20the%20biennale%20is%20to%20interrogate%20the%20two%20sides.%20Dr.%20Alka%20Pande%2C%20artistic%20producer%20and%20chief%20curator%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Museum%20biennale%2C%20believes%20that%20museums%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20important%20cultural%20spaces%20where%20we%20learn%20about%20our%20very%20own%20culture%20and%20civilisation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11160148%2FExterior-of-the-Bihar-museum-1024x574.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11160148%2FExterior-of-the-Bihar-museum-1024x574.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11160148%2FExterior-of-the-Bihar-museum-300x168.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11160148%2FExterior-of-the-Bihar-museum.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672552%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22471%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EExterior%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Museum%20in%20Patna.%20Photo%3A%20Shivam%20Setu%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%E2%80%9CHistory%20of%20Civilization%E2%80%9D%20exhibit%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20museum%20is%20not%20a%20mere%20display%20of%20antiquities%2C%20but%20it%20evokes%20a%20sense%20of%20memory%2C%20exploring%20ideas%20of%20identity%20and%20roots.%20It%20includes%20representation%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20rich%20history%20through%20artefacts%20in%20terracotta%2C%20bronze%2C%20stones%20and%20manuscripts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatna%20lends%20itself%20to%20be%20the%20most%20appropriate%20location%20for%20the%20event.%20Pataliputra%2C%20the%20old%20name%20of%20Patna%2C%20was%20a%20place%20where%20art%20and%20cultural%20glory%20thrived%2C%20and%20the%20region%20was%20the%20centre%20of%20education.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20exhibit%20underscores%20what%20the%20history%20of%20the%20region%20stood%20for%20%E2%80%93%20a%20seat%20of%20power%20that%20reflects%20the%20pluralistic%20nature%20of%20India%20where%20all%20religions%20existed%20side%20by%20side%3B%20Buddhism%2C%20Jainism%2C%20Sikhism%2C%20Hinduism%20and%20Islam.%20The%20museum%20reflects%20that%20inclusiveness%20and%20speaks%20of%20the%20plurality%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20temporary%20exhibits%20uniquely%20keep%20a%20non-Eurocentric%20approach%20through%20the%20selection%20of%20countries%20like%20Nepal%2C%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20Panama%2C%20Israel%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Russia.%20The%20title%20of%20the%20G20%20exhibit%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CTogether%20We%20Art%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20became%20an%20expression%20of%20various%20exhibitions%20within%20the%20biennale%2C%20a%20sort%20of%20meta-narrative%20of%20the%20curatorial%20framework%20of%20the%20number%20of%20exhibitions%20taking%20place%20through%20the%20four%20months%20of%20the%20biennale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20singular%20theme%20that%20binds%20the%20entire%20biennale%2C%20rather%2C%20the%20main%20focus%20in%20this%20edition%20seemed%20to%20be%20to%20immerse%2C%20engage%20and%20enlighten%20all%20art%20enthusiasts%20as%20well%20as%20the%20general%20public.%20The%20programming%20is%20comprehensive%20to%20include%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20shows%20that%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20profound%20significance%20of%20various%20cultures%20and%20art%20forms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdriana%20Bustos%2C%20a%20multidisciplinary%20artist%20who%20currently%20resides%20and%20works%20in%20Buenos%20Aires%2C%20Argentina%2C%20presented%20the%20work%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBestiario%20de%20Indias%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20(Bestiary%20of%20Indias).%20A%20large-scale%20painting%2C%20it%20depicts%20a%20landscape%20populated%20by%20an%20array%20of%20fantastical%20beings%2C%20some%20of%20which%20possess%20a%20hybrid%20nature%2C%20combining%20human%20and%20animal%20characteristics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20490px)%2085vw%2C%20490px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11160847%2FBestiary.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22490%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11160847%2FBestiary.png%20490w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11160847%2FBestiary-225x300.png%20225w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672553%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20narrative%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20images%20and%20stories%20documented%20by%20the%20first%20chroniclers%20who%20arrived%20in%20the%20territories%20that%20later%20came%20to%20be%