With%20over%20a%20dozen%20works%20displayed%2C%20the%20significant%20intervention%20included%20a%20wall%20that%20showcased%20the%20various%20stages%20of%20making%20a%20traditional%20Thanjavur%20painting.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20display%20titled%20%E2%80%9CModern%20Indian%20Painting%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20Salar%20Jung%20Museum%20of%20Hyderabad%20showcases%20the%20culture%20of%20Telangana%20through%20an%20artistic%20lens.%20It%20comprises%20a%20selection%20of%20works%20by%20contemporary%20artists%20responding%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20Telengana%E2%80%99s%20people%20and%20culture.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Nepal%20Art%20Council%20has%20brought%20the%20exhibition%20%E2%80%9CNepal%3A%20Where%20The%20Gods%20Reside%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20biennale.%20Through%20over%2070%20artworks%2C%20the%20display%20aims%20to%20impress%20upon%20visitors%20the%20vastness%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20syncretic%20spiritual%20atmosphere%2C%20as%20the%20abode%20of%20deities.%20The%20most%20striking%20display%20is%20the%20108%20interpretations%20of%20Lord%20Buddha%2C%20made%20in%20traditional%20miniature%20style.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20Russia%20comes%20%E2%80%9CMystic%20Universe%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20show%20offering%20a%20journey%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Efuses%20ancient%20mysticism%20with%20state-of-the-art%20technology.%20Artists%20like%20Julius%20Horstuis%2C%20Luminokaya%20and%20Igor%20Baranko%20created%20a%20distinct%20360%C2%B0%20immersive%20experience%20in%20a%20dome%2C%20with%20technologies%20like%20virtual%20reality%20weaving%20Vedic%20philosophies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20this%2C%20a%20cohesive%20theme%20to%20bind%20the%20various%20shows%20was%20missing.%20Many%20of%20the%20exhibits%20were%20mere%20documentary%C2%A0in%20nature%2C%20like%20the%20presentations%C2%A0on%20%E2%80%9CMaking%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Museum%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9CPatna%2C%20the%20City%20of%20Museums%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9CMaritime%20Museum%20at%20Lothal%E2%80%9D.%20Salar%20Jung%E2%80%99s%20presentation%20was%20underwhelming%20in%20the%20choice%20of%20contemporary%20artists%20to%20represent%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kiran%20Nadar%20Museum%20of%20Art%2C%20Delhi%2C%20is%20the%20knowledge%20partner%2C%20which%20has%20created%20an%20outreach%20plan%20that%20aims%20to%20enhance%20the%20scope%20of%20public%20accessibility%20to%20art%20and%20museum%20culture%20through%20the%20tool%20of%20engagement%20and%20interaction.%20At%20the%20main%20entrance%20lobby%2C%20they%20are%20also%20exhibiting%20two%20installations%2C%20%E2%80%9CTaj%20Mahal%E2%80%9D%20by%20Sudarshan%20Shetty%20and%20%E2%80%9CCheap%20Rice%E2%80%9D%20by%20Subodh%20Gupta.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Frahul-kumar-3%5C%22%3ERahul%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20Fulbright%20Scholar.%20He%20is%20a%20curator%2C%20artist%20and%20an%20art%20journalist%2C%20and%20writes%20on%20global%20contemporary%20visual%20arts.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694433644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fbihar-museum-biennale%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20event%20was%20a%20cross-cultural%20collaboration%2C%20bringing%20in%20various%20Indian%20museums%2C%20from%20Hyderabad%20to%20Mumbai.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20Could%E2%80%99ve%20Ended%20India%E2%80%99s%20Bhopal%20Shame%20at%20the%20G20%20Summit%20But%20He%20Chose%20Not%20To%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08233122%2FF5g5yNWboAAc87B.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECrime%20No.%201104%2F84%20was%20registered%20by%20house%20station%20officer%20Surinder%20Singh%20Thakur%20while%20Union%20Carbide%E2%80%99s%20gas%20disaster%20was%20still%20unfolding%20across%20Bhopal.%20In%20the%20streets%20around%20Hanumanganj%20station%2C%20even%20as%20Thakur%20typed%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Union%20Carbide%E2%80%99%20onto%20the%20list%20of%20prime%20suspects%2C%20hundreds%20of%20innocent%20people%20were%20stumbling%20and%20falling%2C%20groaning%20in%20pain%2C%20choking%20and%20guttering%20out%20their%20final%20breaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20day%20the%20crime%20was%20registered%2C%20five%20local%20junior%20officers%20of%20Union%20Carbide%20India%20Limited%20(UCIL)%20were%20the%20first%20company%20officials%20to%20see%20the%20inside%20of%20a%20jail.%20It%20is%20to%20America%E2%80%99s%20disgrace%2C%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20shame%2C%20that%20they%20remain%20the%20last.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDiligent%20station%20officer%20Thakur%C2%A0%20could%20hardly%20have%20imagined%20that%20a%20crime%20so%20vast%2C%20so%20devastating%2C%20so%20clear%2C%20would%20within%20a%20year%20still%20be%20untried%20and%20unpunished.%20It%20is%20scarcely%20credible%20that%20this%20is%20still%20the%20case%20almost%2040%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20Bhopal%2C%20time%20has%20not%20been%20a%20healer.%20Instead%2C%20over%20the%20decades%2C%20the%20moral%20arc%20of%20Indo-US%20relations%20has%20bent%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20industrial%20massacre%20away%20from%20justice%2C%20from%20scrutiny%2C%20and%20well%20away%20from%20accountability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChief%20accused%20Union%20Carbide%20has%20evaded%20charges%20of%20culpable%20homicide%20and%20other%20serious%20criminal%20offences%20in%20India%20for%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20and%20continues%20to%20hide%20in%20plain%20sight%2C%20inside%20the%20United%20States%20yet%20somehow%2C%20outside%20the%20law.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fbhopal-gas-tragedy-union-carbide-refuses-to-pay-more-sc-says-settlement-cant-be-reopened%5C%22%3EBhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%3A%20Union%20Carbide%20Refuses%20to%20Pay%20More%2C%20SC%20Says%20Settlement%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Be%20Reopened%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20Carbide%20was%20allowed%20to%20sell%20its%20assets%20and%20leave%20India%20in%201994.%20It%20transpires%20that%20Union%20Carbide%20fled%20in%20name%20only%2C%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20now%20known%20that%20it%20organised%20a%20third-party%20company%20to%20continue%20its%20trade%20and%20grow%20its%20Indian%20profits%20while%20still%20evading%20Indian%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Union%20Carbide%20merged%20with%20another%20US%20corporation%2C%20Dow%20Chemical%2C%20in%202001%2C%20the%20clandestine%20Indian%20trade%20continued%2C%20until%20Dow%20finally%20inserted%20itself%20in%20place%20of%20the%20third-party%20company.%20To%20fool%20Indian%20officials%2C%20Dow%20managers%20discussed%20putting%20Dow%20labels%20onto%20products%20manufactured%20by%20Carbide%2C%20later%20claiming%20inb%20Indian%20courts%20that%20Carbide%20remained%2C%20after%20the%20merger%2C%20a%20separate%2C%20independent%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bhopal%20criminal%20court%20has%20not%20bought%20the%20story.%20Since%202013%20it%20has%20issued%20seven%20summonses%20to%20Dow%20to%20attend%20court%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20its%20wholly-owned%20subsidiary%20Union%20Carbide.%20All%20but%20one%20of%20the%20summonses%20have%20followed%20a%20process%20set%20out%20in%20a%20bilateral%20Legal%20Assistance%20Treaty%20signed%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20over%2020%20years%20ago.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20the%20treaty%E2%80%99s%20terms%2C%20to%20summon%20a%20criminal%20accused%20India%20must%20ask%20the%20United%20States%20to%20serve%20papers%20on%20its%20behalf.%20But%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20(DoJ)%20has%20so%20far%20ignored%20or%20obstructed%20every%20single%20notice%20intended%20for%20Dow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20this%20week%2C%20no%20Indian%20or%20US%20official%20has%20raised%20as%20much%20as%20a%20squeak%20about%20this%20reprehensible%20obstruction%20of%20justice.%20Now%2C%20a%20dozen%20elected%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Findia-news%2Fbhopal-gas-tragedy-us-congress-members-call-on-court-to-serve-summons-to-dow-chemical%2F3237183%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520letter%252C%2520signed%2520by%2520members%2CTreaty%2520on%2520Criminal%2520Matters%252C%25202001.%5C%22%3Emembers%20of%20the%20US%20Congress%20have%20called%20on%20the%20American%20justice%20department%20to%20end%20its%20covert%20protection%20of%20Union%20Carbide%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20parent%20Dow%20Inc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbhopal-gas-tragedy-curative-petition%5C%22%3EThe%20Handling%20of%20the%20Bhopal%20Gas%20Tragedy%20Reveals%20Our%20Callousness%20Towards%20Victim-Survivors%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20letter%20to%20the%20United%20States%20Deputy%20Attorney%20General%20insists%20that%20the%20DoJ%20finally%20fulfil%20the%20repeated%20request%20from%20treaty%20partner%20India%20to%20serve%20summons%20to%20Dow%2C%20which%20is%20required%20in%20Bhopal%20court%20on%20October%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20letter%20could%20hardly%20be%20more%20timely.%20President%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20attendance%20at%20the%20G20%C2%A0%20provided%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20the%20ideal%20opportunity%20to%20directly%20address%20Dow%20and%20the%20US%20DoJ%E2%80%99s%20scofflaw%20contempt%20for%20Indian%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20their%20letter%2C%20the%20US%20Congress%20members%20state%20that%20the%20DoJ%E2%80%99s%20inaction%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccreating%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ean%20indelible%20stain%20upon%20our%20nation%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20for%20upholding%20international%20legal%20and%20moral%20standards%20that%20must%20be%20corrected.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20PM%20of%20what%20is%20claimed%20to%20be%20an%20assertive%20new%20India%20remains%20deafeningly%20silent%20on%20the%20violated%20rights%20of%20the%20thousands%20of%20Indian%20citizens%20killed%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20maimed%20in%20Bhopal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20staging%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20on%20which%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20eyes%20rested%2C%20offered%20him%20an%20unprecedented%20opportunity%20to%20join%20the%20principled%20stand%20of%20the%2012%20US%20Congress%20members.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20let%20it%20go.%20In%20Bhopal%2C%20where%20they%20have%20waited%2039%20years%20for%20just%20one%20courageous%20champion%20in%20Delhi%2C%20there%20is%20little%20enough%20breath%20left%20to%20bate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMadhumita%20Dutta%20is%20a%20volunteer%20with%20the%20International%20Campaign%20for%20Justice%20in%20Bhopal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694433609000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08233122%2FF5g5yNWboAAc87B.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-couldve-ended-indias-bhopal-shame-at-the-g20-summit-but-he-chose-not-to%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20attendance%20at%20the%20G20%20provided%20Modi%20the%20ideal%20opportunity%20to%20directly%20address%20Union%20Carbide%20and%20the%20US%20DoJ%E2%80%99s%20scofflaw%20contempt%20for%20Indian%20justice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmo