how%2F103578925.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%3A%20What%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Declaration%20Means%20for%20Global%20Digital%20Futures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133650%2F11.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20diplomats%20and%20bureaucrats%20are%20celebrating%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.g20.org%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fgtwenty%2Fgtwenty_new%2Fdocument%2FG20-New-Delhi-Leaders-Declaration.pdf%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20Declaration%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20the%20outcome%20of%20a%20consensus%20amongst%20all%20G20%20member%20countries.%20This%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20win%20for%20India%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20aspect%20of%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructures%20(DPIs)%2C%20which%20are%20being%20seen%20as%20an%20Indian%20innovation%20in%20information%20technology.%20This%20comes%20after%20the%20a%20US-India%20joint%20statement%20agreeing%20to%20develop%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findia-us-global-digital-development-rights%5C%22%3EUS-India%20Global%20Digital%20Development%20Partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20promoting%20DPIs%20in%20the%20month%20of%20June%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20declaration%E2%80%99s%20emphasis%20on%20DPI%20recommends%20building%20a%20%E2%80%9Csafe%2C%20secure%2C%20trusted%2C%20accountable%20and%20inclusive%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20respectful%20of%20human%20rights%2C%20personal%20data%2C%20privacy%20and%20intellectual%20property%20rights%20can%20foster%20resilience%2C%20and%20enable%20service%20delivery%20and%20innovation%E2%80%9D.%20The%20consensus%20on%20DPI%20is%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%20i.%20Welcome%20to%20the%20G20%20Framework%20for%20Systems%20of%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%2C%20a%20voluntary%20and%20suggested%20framework%20for%20the%20development%2C%20deployment%20and%20governance%20of%20DPI.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Eii.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EWelcome%20India%E2%80%99s%20plan%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20a%20Global%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20Repository%20(GDPIR)%2C%20a%20virtual%20repository%20of%20DPI%2C%20voluntarily%20shared%20by%20G20%20members%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Eiii.%20Take%20note%20of%20the%20Indian%20President%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20of%20the%20One%20Future%20Alliance%20(OFA)%2C%20a%20voluntary%20initiative%20aimed%20to%20build%20capacity%2C%20and%20provide%20technical%20assistance%20and%20adequate%20funding%20support%20for%20implementing%20DPI%20in%20LMICs%20%5Blow-%20and%20middle-income%20countries%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20language%20of%20voluntary%20DPI%20is%20something%20that%20has%20been%20evolved%20in%20India%20with%20its%20digital%20identity%20project%20Aadhaar%2C%20where%20it%20was%20always%20voluntary%20until%20it%20became%20mandatory%20for%20the%20entire%20population.%20Similarly%20with%20DPIs%2C%20we%20are%20being%20suggested%20a%20voluntary%20framework%20that%20will%20actually%20be%20forced%20on%20the%20world%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20421px)%2085vw%2C%20421px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22421%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22294%5C%22%3EIndia%20is%20clearly%20taking%20the%20lead%20on%20this%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20a%20repository%20of%20DPIs%20ideally%20to%20share%20source%20codes%20of%20projects%20from%20India.%20India%E2%80%99s%20sharing%20of%20these%20resources%20will%20allow%20it%20to%20set%20the%20standards%20for%20these%20DPIs%20rather%20than%20allowing%20alternative%20solutions%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20of%20the%20One%20Future%20Alliance%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20US-India%20Global%20Digital%20Development%20Partnership%20to%20develop%20and%20fund%20DPIs%20in%20low-%20and%20middle-income%20countries.%20This%20alliance%20becomes%20a%20new%20player%20backed%20by%20India%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20ID4D%2C%20ID4Africa%20and%20other%20digital%20ldentity-led%20initiatives%20that%20have%20been%20backed%20by%20the%20World%20Bank%20and%20UNDP.%20If%20more%20countries%20join%20the%20alliance%20with%20sovereign%20funds%20guaranteed%20by%20their%20nation%E2%80%99s%20wealth%2C%20it%20is%20easier%20for%20institutions%20like%20the%20World%20Bank%20to%20fund%20digital%20identities%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fen%2Fcontent%2Fdigital-cooperation-roadmap%2F%5C%22%3EUN%20Secretary%20General%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20for%20Digital%20Co-operation%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20recommend%20digital%20public%20goods%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20towards%20promoting%20DPIs%20are%20all%20leading%20towards%20a%20new%20international%20consensus%20of%20a%20world%20where%20every%20individual%20is%20datafied%20and%20commodified%20under%20the%20pretext%20of%20financial%20inclusion%20and%20SDGs.%20The%20UNDP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20assisting%20India%E2%80%99s%20G20%20along%20with%20several%20philanthropies%20like%20the%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20has%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.undp.org%2Fpress-releases%2Fg20-digital-ministers-recognize-digital-public-infrastructure-accelerator-global-goals%5C%22%3Eplaybook%20on%20definitions%20of%20DPIs%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20G20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20playbook%20by%20UNDP%20is%20again%20aimed%20for%20low-%20and%20middle-income%20countries%2C%20which%20are%20potential%20trade%20partners%20for%20India%20to%20supply%20its%20Aadhar%20model.%20The%20playbook%20prepared%20by%20Aapti%20Institute%20and%20Centre%20for%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructure%20in%20Bangalore%20describes%20a%20glossary%20of%20terms%20evolved%20in%20Bangalore%20and%20internationally%20through%20a%20host%20of%20alliances%20to%20sell%20DPIs%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20definitions%20of%20digital%20public%20goods%2C%20digital%20public%20infrastructures%20and%20India%E2%80%99s%20claims%20of%20using%20open%20source%20to%20build%20these%20glorified%20databases%20is%20a%20branding%20and%20marketing%20strategy%20to%20export%20its%20technologies%20to%20other%20countries.%20One%20that%20has%20been%20successfully%20executed%20through%20the%20help%20of%20a%20host%20of%20multilateral%20organisations%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDPIs%20at%20best%20can%20be%20described%20as%20software%20infrastructures%20that%20power%20economic%20and%20governance%20transactions%20to%20promote%20market%20economy%20by%20commodifying%20citizens%20using%20their%20digital%20identity%20as%20the%20foundation.%20They%20are%20glorified%20credit%20bureaus%20that%20constantly%20record%20data%20of%20citizens%20to%20be%20shared%20with%20markets%20backed%20by%20the%20nation%20state%E2%80%99s%20powers%20of%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20DPIs%20are%20being%20termed%20an%20Indian%20innovation%2C%20globally%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fmagazine%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2Festonia-the-digital-republic%5C%22%3EEstonia%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20first%20experimented%20the%20digital%20identity%20solutions.%20India%20gave%20digital%20identity%20the%20scale%20and%20recognition%20by%20forcing%20it%20on%20its%20population%20and%20branding%20it%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20to%20adopt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%20standards%20bodies%20like%20World%20Wide%20Web%20Consortium%2C%20Unicode%20Consortium%2C%20Open%20Geospatial%20Consortium%20and%20Internet%20Governance%20Forum%20were%20places%20where%20new%20standards%20for%20IT%20and%20internet%20governance%20have%20been%20discussed%2C%20debated%20and%20settled.%20These%20bodies%20have%20been%20historically%20in%20the%20global%20north%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20several%20countries%20in%20the%20global%20south%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20development%20of%20digital%20futures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20India%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20towards%20a%20One%20Future%20Alliance%2C%20there%20will%20ideally%20be%20an%20international%20body%20that%20would%20be%20set%20up%20with%20India%20determining%20governance%20and%20standards%20with%20DPIs.%20If%20one%20were%20to%20seriously%20look%20at%20these%20systems%2C%20they%20are%20centralised%20systems%20that%20have%20been%20particularly%20designed%20this%20particular%20way%20to%20build%20a%20unified%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20solutions%20designed%20with%20the%20motto%20of%20One%20Nation%20One%20Solution%20are%20not%20a%20BJP%20phenomenon%20but%20were%20necessary%20for%20the%20market%20economy%20to%20consolidate%20a%20billion%20customers.%20One%20Nation-One%20Identity%2C%20One%20Taxation%2C%20One%20Payment%20System%2C%20One%20Toll%20System%2C%20One%20Mobility%20Card%2C%20One%20Ration%20Card%2C%20One%20Electoral%20System%20are%20others%20that%20have%20been%20pushed%20to%20build%20One%20Unified%20Market.%20The%20idea%20of%20360-degree%20profiling%20and%20tracking%20populations%20from%20their%20birth%20to%20death%20has%20been%20pushed%20by%20the%20market%20in%20the%20name%20of%20real-time%20governance%20to%20power%20this%20One%20Nation%20as%20a%20Single%20Market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effects%20of%20these%20systems%20with%20respect%20towards%20centralisation%20of%20power%20and%20increased%20use%20of%20surveillance%20in%20our%20governance%20systems%20were%20completely%20endorsed%20by%20market%20actors%20like%20World%20Bank%2C%20Bill%20and%20Melinda%20Gates%20Foundation%2C%20Omidyar%20Network%2C%20Nilekani%20Philanthropies%20among%20others.%20These%20effects%20were%20not%20entirely%20political%20as%20they%20seem%20with%20post%2026%2F11%20India%E2%80%99s%20interest%20to%20develop%20surveillance%20systems%20or%20rather%20there%20was%20a%20fusion%20of%20these%20interests%20globally%20and%20within%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%20and%20the%20world%20decide%20to%20adopt%20these%20systems%2C%20you%20will%20witness%20more%20low-%20and%20middle-income%20countries%20gain%20power%20and%20control%20over%20their%20populations.%20India%20is%20increasingly%20pushing%20these%20systems%20into%20countries%20with%20ethnic%20conflicts%20and%20dictatorial%20power%20setups%20like%20Ethiopia%2C%20the%20Philippines%2C%20Myanmar%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%20What%20a%20digital%20identity-led%20model%20would%20mean%20for%20these%20countries%20is%20increasingly%20visible%20in%20India%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justsecurity.org%2F88061%2Findias-digital-governance-model-fails-on-rights%2F%5C%22%3Edigital%20authoritarianism%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20is%20reflected%20over%20issues%20of%20representation%20and%20repression%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20several%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20North%20like%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20Union%20endorse%20these%20solutions%20for%20countries%20in%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20they%20will%20not%20risk%20corrupting%20their%20systems%20entirely%20without%20the%20right%20safeguards.%20In%20his%20last%20blog%20for%20Omidyar%20Network%2C%20C.V.%20Madhukar%2C%20who%20championed%20these%20digital%20identity%20solutions%20in%20India%2C%20wrote%20about%20the%20need%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fomidyar-network%2Freimagining-digital-public-infrastructure-is-no-longer-just-a-development-agenda-6c3915d20598%5C%22%3Ere-imagination%20of%20DPIs%20for%20US%20and%20Europe%20with%20better%20safeguards%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20quote%20Madhukar%2C%20%E2%80%9CSafeguards%20in%20the%20form%20of%20technology%2C%20law%2C%20and%20institutions%20must%20drive%20the%20norms%20and%20behavior%20of%20both%20the%20designers%20of%20technology%20and%20its%20users%2C%20and%20the%20government%20must%20guarantee%20these%20protections.%E2%80%9D%20While%20he%20continues%20to%20promote%20Digital%20Public%20Infrastructures%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.codevelop.fund%2Fabout%5C%22%3ECo-Develop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20anyone%20will%20look%20at%20these%20warnings%20as%20India%20brands%20its%20solutions%20as%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694431670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F08133650%2F11.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fg20-what-the-new-delhi-declaration-means-for-global-digital-futures%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20language%20of%20voluntary%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20is%20something%20that%20has%20been%20evolved%20in%20India%20with%20Aadhaar%2C%20where%20it%20was%20always%20voluntary%20until%20it%20became%20mandatory%20for%20the%20entire%20population.%20Similarly%20with%20DPIs%2C%20we%20are%20being%20suggested%20a%20voluntary%20framework%20that%20will%20actually%20be%20forced%20on%20the%20world%20population.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saad%20Bilgrami%20on%20'Panchayat%203'%3A%20Exclusive!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694430722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103576084%2Cimgsize-26710.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fsaad-bilgrami-on-panchayat-3-its-going-to-be-very-different-from-what-ive-played-in-gharwapsi-khuda-haafiz-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F103576097.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103576097.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActor%20Saad%20Bilgrami%2C%20known%20for%20his%20roles%20in%20various%20web%20series%2C%20is%20receiving%20acclaim%20for%20his%20recent%20projects.%20He%20discusses%20the%20importance%20of%20his%20upcoming%20project%20'Panchayat%203'%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20OTT%20platforms%2C%20and%20his%20other%20upcoming%20projects.%20Bilgrami%20shares%20that%20'Panchayat%203'%20is%20significant%20to%20him%20as%20his%20father%20had%20enjoyed%20watching%20the%20previous%20seasons%20while%20recovering%20from%20a%20heart%20attack.%20He%20expresses%20gratitude%20for%20the%20opportunities%20provided%20by%20OTT%20platforms%20to%20actors%20like%20him.%20Bilgrami%20also%20talks%20about%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20outsiders%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20mentions%20his%20future%20projects%20including%20'Gullak'%20season%204%20and%20'Lakhan%20Leela%20Bhargava'%20season%202.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Vaishali%20Rathod%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fsaad-bilgrami-on-panchayat-3-its-going-to-be-very-different-from-what-ive-played-in-gharwapsi-khuda-haafiz-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F103576097.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reliance%20Jio%20launches%20fire%20safety%20and%20prevention%20campaign%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694430635000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F03%2Ffull%2F1680506288-648.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-jio-launches-fire-safety-and-prevention-campaign-in-delhi-ncr-123091100610_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reliance%20Jio%20has%20embarked%20on%20a%20fire%20safety%20and%20fire%20prevention%20campaign%20aimed%20at%20enhancing%20safety%20measures%20across%20its%20network%20sites%20throughout%20Delhi%20NCR%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Freliance-jio-launches-fire-safety-and-prevention-campaign-in-delhi-ncr-123091100610_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22General%20Naravane%20Is%20Mistaken%20%E2%80%93%20'Strategic%20Depth'%20Has%20No%20Relevance%20Against%20China%20or%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F16220815%2FScreen-Shot-2019-12-16-at-10.07.48-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-indias-strategic-depth-is-of-little-value-from-pakistan-to-china-borders%2F1745319%2F%5C%22%3Erecent%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20chief%20of%20army%20staff%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%20has%20argued%20that%20since%20India%20does%20not%20have%20%E2%80%98strategic%20depth%E2%80%99%20against%20China%2C%20the%20army%20will%20need%20to%20maintain%20heavy%20forward%20deployment%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC).%20This%20argument%20displays%20ignorance%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20threats%20and%20options%20on%20the%20two%20military%20lines.%20Not%20only%20is%20the%20concept%20of%20strategic%20depth%20irrelevant%20against%20China%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20but%20army%E2%80%99s%20relevance%20also%20will%20be%20minimal%20in%20a%20war%20with%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army%20(PLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Strategic%20depth%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20front-line%20and%20an%20army%E2%80%99s%20base%20(away%20from%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20assets%20and%20vulnerable%20areas)%20where%20it%20has%20its%20operational%20sustenance%20(troops%20and%20war%20waging%20materiel)%20for%20war.%20If%20this%20distance%20is%20more%2C%20the%20frontline%20may%20be%20held%20lightly%20to%20tempt%20the%20enemy%20to%20walk%20into%20a%20killing%20zone%20with%20stretched%20lines%20of%20communication.%20When%20this%20luxury%20is%20not%20available%2C%20the%20frontline%20needs%20heavy%20deployment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%E2%80%98strategic%20depth%E2%80%99%20is%20about%20tactics%2C%20and%20army-led%20defensive%20operations%2C%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20war%20will%20be%20campaign%20level%20offensive%20operations%20which%20will%20completely%20bypass%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20tactical%20level%20of%20war.%20Recall%2C%20the%201991%20operation%20Desert%20Storm%20by%20the%20US%20military%20against%20the%20Iraqi%20military%2C%20where%20there%20were%20neither%20tactical%20combat%20nor%20the%20need%20for%20%E2%80%98strategic%20depth%E2%80%99.%20After%2043%20days%20of%20air%20campaign%20by%20the%20US%20at%20the%20operational%20level%20across%20the%20entire%20war%20theatre%2C%20the%20tactics%20were%20limited%20to%20100%20hours%20of%20mopping%20up%20operations.%20The%20brave%20and%20battle%20hardened%20Iraqi%20Republican%20Guards%20(who%20fought%2010%20years%E2%80%99%20war%20with%20Iran)%20were%20decimated%20from%20the%20air%20by%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20with%20support%20from%20outer%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20major%20power%2C%20US%2C%20and%20medium%20power%2C%20Iraq%2C%20the%20PLA%20war%20with%20the%20Indian%20military%20will%20be%20expansive%20and%20will%20go%20beyond%20the%20combat%20theatre.%20Worse%2C%20the%20PLA%20has%20capabilities%20to%20combat%20in%20six%20war-domains%20(land%2C%20air%2C%20sea%2C%20cyber%2C%20electromagnetic%20spectrum%2C%20outer%20space)%20compared%20with%20Indian%20military%E2%80%99s%20three%20domains%20of%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20military%20has%20no%20answer%20for%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20war%20with%20nine%20exceptional%20characteristics.%20One%2C%20in%20a%20lightening%20and%20intense%20campaign%20without%20any%20warning%20time%2C%20the%20PLA%20will%20combat%20simultaneously%20across%20the%20war%20zone%20(whole%20of%20nation)%20and%20combat%20zone%20(across%20the%20entire%20theatre%20of%20operation).%20The%20war%20zone%20will%20witness%20coordinated%20employment%20of%20cyber%2C%20outer%20space%20and%20information%20operations%20(misinformation%2C%20disinformation%2C%20and%20synthetic%20reality%20involving%20fake%20texts%20and%20deepfake%20videos%20on%20social%20media).%20By%20destroying%2C%20disrupting%2C%20and%20poisoning%20data%20in%20cyberspace%2C%20these%20operations%20will%20bring%20civilian%20life%20to%20a%20standstill%20with%20maximum%20cognitive%20pressure%20on%20the%20political%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22On%20the%20India-China%20Border%2C%20Disengagement%20Is%20Not%20Resolution%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fon-the-india-china-border-disengagement-is-not-resolution%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20India-China%20Border%2C%20Disengagement%20Is%20Not%20Resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20in%20the%20combat%20zone%2C%20the%20PLA%20will%20exercise%20total%20war%20control%20by%20dominating%20the%20battlespace%20comprising%20cyberspace%2C%20Electro%20Magnetic%20Space%20(EMS)%2C%20and%20outer%20space%20domains%2C%20which%20will%20snap%20communications%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20command.%20Unlike%20the%20Indian%20military%2C%20PLA%20has%20capability%20to%20combat%2C%20compete%2C%20and%20confront%20in%20these%20three%20critical%20war%20domains%20which%20work%20under%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20Strategic%20Support%20Force%20(PLASSF)%20and%20report%20to%20the%20Joint%20Staff%20Department%20(JSD)%20responsible%20to%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20highest%20body%2C%20the%20Central%20Military%20Commission%20headed%20by%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20The%20PLA%2C%20therefore%2C%20will%20exert%20control%20over%20war%20aims%2C%20war%20concepts%2C%20speed%2C%20tempo%2C%20intensity%20and%20outcome.%20This%20involves%20seizing%20the%20initiative%2C%20paralysing%20the%20enemy%2C%20dominating%20the%20escalation%20ladder%2C%20and%20laying%20grounds%20for%20early%20war%20termination%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20own%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%2C%20since%20the%20Indian%20defence%20services%20are%20not%20even%20fully%20networked%20and%20hence%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20continuum%20of%20cyberspace%2C%20EMS%2C%20and%20outer%20space%20to%20be%20destroyed%20or%20disabled%20by%20the%20SSF%2C%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20Rocket%20Force%20(PLARF)%20will%20destroy%20the%20partially%20networked%20command%2C%20control%2C%20and%20communication%20centres.%20With%20an%20impressive%20inventory%20of%20ballistic%2C%20hypersonic%2C%20and%20cruise%20missiles%2C%20the%20PLARF%20working%20closely%20with%20PLA%20Air%20Force%20(PLAAF)%20bombers%20and%20PLA%20Army%20(PLAA)%20long%20range%20precision%20artillery%20fire%20will%20unleash%20intense%20salvos%20on%20IAF%E2%80%99s%20main%2C%20diversionary%2C%20and%20hinterland%20bases%2C%20blowing%20up%20ammunition%20and%20fuel%20dumps%20to%20ensure%20that%20enemy%20combat%20aircraft%20remain%20grounded.%20Priority%20would%20be%20accorded%20to%20communication%20towers%2C%20power%20centres%2C%20bridges%2C%20tunnels%2C%20radar%20sites%2C%20air%20defence%20systems%2C%20and%20command%20and%20control%20hubs.%20Since%20most%20Indian%20targets%20will%20be%20static%2C%20well-mapped%2C%20and%20watched%2C%20it%20will%20not%20be%20difficult%20for%20the%20PLA%20to%20hit%20them%20with%20precision.%20Working%20together%2C%20under%20the%20JSD%2C%20the%20PLARF%20and%20PLASSF%20will%20render%20the%20Indian%20military%20blind%20with%20no%20communications%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20command%20leading%20to%20command%20breakdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%2C%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20massive%20sensors%20network%20on%20land%2C%20air%2C%20and%20in%20outer%20space%20will%20provide%20real-time%20situational%20awareness%20of%20the%20combat%20zone%2C%20operational%20logistics%20lifeline%20(or%20what%20Naravane%20calls%20communication%20zones%20where%20operational%20sustenance%20will%20travel)%2C%20and%20high%20value%20targets%20in%20the%20hinterland.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20place%20to%20hide%20from%20the%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20accurate%20firepower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%2C%20the%20PLA%20and%20Indian%20military%20will%20combat%20at%20different%20tempo%20and%20speed%20of%20war.%20The%20PLA%E2%80%99s%20tempo%20of%20war%20will%20be%20determined%20by%20the%20speed%20of%20light%20through%20cyberspace%2C%20and%20conventional%20surface-to-surface%20missiles%20with%20the%20ability%20to%20hit%20targets%20thousands%20of%20kilometres%20away%20at%20speeds%20of%20Mach%2020.%20One%20Mach%2C%20which%20is%20the%20speed%20of%20sound%2C%20is%201%2C235%20km%20per%20hour%2C%20and%20the%20speed%20of%20light%2C%20which%20is%20in%20nanoseconds%2C%20is%20300%2C000%20km%20per%20second.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20traditional%20missiles%2C%20bombs%2C%20and%20munitions%2C%20the%20PLA%20will%20place%20a%20premium%20on%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20cyber%20warfare%2C%20and%20directed%20energy%20weapons%20(laser%20and%20microwave%20weapons)%20operating%20at%20the%20speed%20of%20light.%20The%20Indian%20military%E2%80%99s%20fastest%20platforms%20are%20its%20conventional%20BrahMos%20cruise%20missile%20with%20maximum%20speed%20of%20Mach%203.7%2C%20and%20the%20Rafale%20aircraft%20with%20the%20speed%20of%202%2C450%20kmph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%2C%20the%20PLA%20has%20an%20unmatched%20inventory%20of%20UAVs%20(unmanned%20aerial%20vehicles)%20and%20UCAVs%20(unmanned%20combat%20aerial%20vehicles)%20with%20all%20its%20services.%20It%20has%20loitering%20munitions%2C%20mini%20drones%20with%20facial%20recognition%20capabilities%20(slaughter-bots)%2C%20legacy%20aircraft%20converted%20into%20Kamikaze%20drones%2C%20and%20swarm%20drones%20with%20front-end%20computing%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%2C%20with%20the%20entire%20combat%20zone%20in%20disarray%20with%20PLASSF%2C%20PLARF%2C%20and%20PLAAF%20accurate%20fires%2C%20the%20PLA%20would%20use%20its%20special%20forces%2C%20heliborne%20forces%2C%20aviation%20brigades%2C%20and%20air%20assault%20brigades%20for%20vertical%20envelopment%20and%20air%20insertion%20missions%20right%20till%20the%20Brahmaputra%20valley.%20The%20PLA%20is%20assessed%20to%20have%20over%20150%2C000%20airborne%20combat%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEight%2C%20China%20has%20a%20self-sufficient%20and%20vibrant%20defence%20industrial%20base%2C%20something%20that%20India%20lacks.%20As%20evident%20from%20the%20ongoing%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20the%20NATO%20nations%20are%20unable%20to%20match%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20defence%20industrial%20infrastructure%20which%20can%20meet%20war%20surge%20requirements%20of%20tanks%2C%20guns%2C%20missiles%2C%20and%20specialised%20munitions.%20A%20nation%20without%20indigenous%20war%20surge%20capabilities%20cannot%20win%20a%20war%2C%20whether%20limited%20or%20protracted%20against%20an%20enemy%20which%20has%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22What%20Lies%20Behind%20Rajnath%20Singh's%20Calls%20for%20the%20Crossing%20the%20LoC%20%E2%80%93%20War%20or%20Politics%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-lies-behind-rajnath-singhs-calls-for-the-crossing-the-loc-war-or-politics%5C%22%3EWhat%20Lies%20Behind%20Rajnath%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Calls%20for%20the%20Crossing%20the%20LoC%20%E2%80%93%20War%20or%20Politics%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20nine%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20nuclear%20weapons%20will%20have%20no%20use%20in%20a%20war%20with%20China.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20PLA%20campaign%20based%20on%20military%20strategy%20of%20cognitive%20defeat%20will%20happen%20at%20hyper-speed%20leaving%20the%20political%20and%20military%20leadership%20groping%20in%20the%20dark%20for%20lack%20of%20information.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20if%20India%20tries%20to%20flex%20nuclear%20muscle%20or%20move%20its%20nuclear%20assets%2C%20China%20could%20exercise%20one%20of%20the%20three%20options%3A%20destroy%20Indian%20nukes%E2%80%99%20kill%20chain%20with%20cyber%2C%20electronic%2C%20or%20long-range%20precision%20hypersonic%20glide%20vehicles%3B%20threaten%20to%20use%20low%20yield%20nukes%20in%20campaign%20as%20a%20warning%20signal%3B%20or%20adapt%20to%20Launch%20on%20Warning%20(LOW)%20nuclear%20posture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20becomes%20clear%20from%20the%20above%20that%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98strategic%20depth%E2%80%99%20and%20even%20the%20lead%20role%20for%20land%20forces%20(army)%20is%20meaningless.%20Using%20its%20far%20superior%20technology%20and%20war%20concepts%2C%20the%20PLA%20has%20the%20capability%20to%20wrest%20India%E2%80%99s%20state%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20with%20minimal%20casualties%20of%20its%20own%20forces%20in%20a%20short%2C%20swift%2C%20and%20intense%20multi-domain%20decisive%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20Naravane%20has%20got%20mixed%20up%20in%20war%20and%20%E2%80%98grey%20zone%E2%80%99%20operations%20done%20below%20the%20war%20threshold%20in%20peacetime.%20The%20June%2015%2C%202020%20Galwan%20clash%20which%20was%20the%20high%20point%20of%20grey%20zone%20operations%20forced%20the%20two%20sides%20to%20reinforce%20their%20front-line%20capabilities.%20Situation%20for%20the%20Indian%20army%20got%20complicated%20by%20China%E2%80%99s%20boundary%20law%20which%20became%20effective%20on%20January%201%2C%202022.%20By%20stating%20this%20law%2C%20China%20has%20framed%20the%20border%20dispute%20as%20an%20issue%20of%20its%20sovereignty%2C%20which%20will%20be%20defended%20at%20all%20costs.%20Thus%2C%20if%20the%20Indian%20army%20manages%20to%20make%20tactical%20gain%20on%20the%20LAC%2C%20the%20PLA%20under%20its%20law%2C%20will%20be%20obliged%20to%20use%20arms%20by%20ending%20grey%20zone%20operations.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20PLA%20will%20permanently%20maintain%20pressure%20on%20the%20LAC%20with%20its%20grey%20zone%20operations%2C%20thereby%20ensuring%20that%20the%20Indian%20Army%20is%20unable%20to%20reduce%20its%20forces%20in%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20These%20grey%20zone%20operations%20will%20rise%20and%20ebb%20depending%20on%20China%E2%80%99s%20relations%20with%20India%20at%20the%20given%20time%2C%20irrespective%20of%20a%20mutually%20agreed%20peaceful%20LAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ultimate%20irony%20for%20the%20Indian%20army%20is%20that%20it%20needs%20large%20numbers%20in%20peacetime%20for%20grey%20zone%20operations%20against%20PLA.%20But%20in%20an%20event%20of%20a%20war%2C%20these%20large%20numbers%20will%20become%20a%20liability%2C%20as%20they%20will%20have%20little%20operational%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20where%20both%20sides%20will%20fight%20war%20of%20attrition%2C%20the%20concept%20of%20%E2%80%98strategic%20space%E2%80%99%20has%20become%20irrelevant.%20For%20one%2C%20since%20both%20military%20lines%20are%20active%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20the%20Indian%20military%20with%20limited%20capabilities%20and%20capacities%20to%20even%20consider%20expanding%20a%20war%20with%20Pakistan%20beyond%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20to%20the%20international%20border%2C%20where%20in%20the%20desert%2C%20Naravane%20talks%20of%20acquiring%20%E2%80%98strategic%20depth.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20another%2C%20Indian%20military%20simply%20does%20not%20have%20credible%20conventional%20capabilities%20to%20fight%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20two-front%20war.%20If%20India%20had%20credible%20war%20waging%20or%20counter-offensive%20capabilities%20against%20Pakistan%2C%20Rawalpindi%20would%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20review%20its%20proxy%20war%20strategy%20as%20a%20costly%20adventure%20which%20could%20boomerang.%20It%20is%20regrettable%20that%20Indian%20army%20leadership%20has%20failed%20to%20create%20credible%20conventional%20deterrence%20against%20Pakistan%20since%201990%20when%20trouble%20started%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPravin%20Sawhney%20is%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Last%20War%3A%20How%20AI%20Will%20Shape%20India%E2%80%99s%20Final%20Showdown%20With%20China%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694429567000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F16220815%2FScreen-Shot-2019-12-16-at-10.07.48-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fgeneral-naravane-is-mistaken-strategic-depth-has-no-relevance-against-china-or-pakistan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Army%E2%80%99s%20relevance%20will%20be%20minimal%20in%20a%20war%20with%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Liberation%20Army.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Byju's%20puts%20Epic%2C%20Great%20Learning%20on%20sale%20to%20raise%20%24800million-%241billion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694429361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F11%2Ffull%2F1694414512-9722.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbyju-s-puts-epic-great-learning-on-sale-to-raise-800million-1billion-123091100664_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Byju's%20is%20hoping%20to%20earn%20between%20%24400-%24500%20million%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20Epic%2C%20which%20is%20a%20US-based%20kids'%20learning%20company%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbyju-s-puts-epic-great-learning-on-sale-to-raise-800million-1billion-123091100664_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Public%20sector%20company%20ITI%20develops%20its%20own%20branded%20laptop%2C%20micro%20PC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694428232000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-10%2F06%2Ffull%2F1665025650-4024.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpublic-sector-company-iti-develops-its-own-branded-laptop-micro-pc-123091100542_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Public%20sector%20telecommunications%20company%20ITI%20Limited%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20has%20developed%20its%20own%20branded%20laptop%20and%20micro%20PC%20with%20international%20standards%20and%20launched%20them%20in%20the%20market%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpublic-sector-company-iti-develops-its-own-branded-laptop-micro-pc-123091100542_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20World%20of%20Village%20Deities%20in%20Karnataka%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11154223%2Fimage-1312.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ESiddalingaiah%2C%20folklorist%20and%20Dalit%20leader%2C%20could%20talk%20about%20village%20deities%20for%20hours.%20His%20extensive%20research%20and%20travel%20within%20Karnataka%20had%20acquainted%20him%20intimately%20with%20their%20myths%20and%20festivals.%20The%20devotees%20of%20a%20goddess%20were%20once%20keen%20to%20build%20a%20small%20temple%20for%20her.%20But%20the%20goddess%20spurned%20the%20idea.%20The%20perplexed%20devotees%20begged%20her%20for%20an%20explanation.%20She%20asked%20them%3A%20%E2%80%9CDoes%20everyone%20have%20a%20house%3F%E2%80%9D%20One%20of%20the%20devotees%20said%20he%20did%20not%20have%20one.%20She%20then%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20a%20house%20until%20all%20of%20you%20have%20one.%E2%80%9D%20Village%20deities%20cherish%20freedom.%20A%20goddess%20once%20discouraged%20her%20devotees%20from%20building%20a%20shrine%20for%20her.%20She%20wanted%20to%20be%20left%20free%20to%20wander%20as%20she%20pleased%20whereas%20the%20shrine%20door%20would%20restrict%20her%20movements.%20The%20doorless%20shrine%20her%20devotees%20then%20built%20for%20her%20still%20exists%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20devotees%20of%20another%20goddess%2C%20Bisilamma%2C%20were%20also%20keen%20to%20build%20a%20shrine%20for%20her.%20The%20goddess%20pleaded%20with%20them%20to%20build%20one%20without%20a%20roof.%20She%20clarified%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20shiver%20in%20the%20cold%2C%20burn%20in%20the%20sun%20and%20get%20drenched%20in%20the%20rains.%E2%80%9D%20Identifying%20with%20the%20hardship%20of%20those%20struggling%20for%20shelter%2C%20she%20invited%20suffering%20for%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20205px)%2085vw%2C%20205px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11140434%2Fimage-1307-205x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22205%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11140434%2Fimage-1307-205x300.png%20205w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11140434%2Fimage-1307.png%20370w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672518%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAnother%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20by%20Chandan%20Gowda.%20(Simon%20%26amp%3B%20Schuster%20India%2C%20September%2012%2C%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiddalingaiah%20realized%20at%20a%20young%20age%20that%20the%20god-human%20relation%20was%20more%20intimate%20and%20humane%20among%20the%20lower%20castes%20and%20villagers.%C2%A0Usually%2C%20purohits%20are%20the%20intermediaries%20between%20the%20gods%20and%20the%20upper%20caste%20devotees.%20Only%20they%20are%20allowed%20inside%20the%20inner%20sanctum%20of%20a%20temple%20while%20the%20devotees%20offer%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20deity%20from%20a%20distance.%20In%20contrast%2C%20Siddalingaiah%20observed%2C%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20god%20and%20the%20devotees%20in%20folk%20religion%20is%20much%20less%2C%20if%20not%20non-existent.%20There%20is%20freedom%20to%20scold%2C%20criticize%20and%20even%20condemn%20gods.%20An%20elderly%C2%A0person%20once%20asked%20a%20deity%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20people%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhere%20were%20you%20all%20these%20days%3F%20Have%20you%20forgotten%20us%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20goddess%20retorted%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20yours%20the%20only%20village%3F%20I%20need%20to%20look%20after%20the%20seven%20worlds.%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20difficult%20my%20work%20is%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20elderly%20person%20persisted%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20so%20hard.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20see%20that%3F%E2%80%99%20The%20goddess%20shot%20back%2C%20%E2%80%98Am%20I%20working%20any%C2%A0less%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeities%20from%20different%20villages%20can%20be%20siblings%20or%20enjoy%20any%20other%20kin%20relation.%20Siddalingaiah%E2%80%99s%20study%2C%20%3Cem%3EGrama%20Devategalu%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Village%20Deities%2C%201997)%2C%20records%20a%20story%20of%20sister%20deities.%20The%20childless%20deity%2C%20Madduramma%2C%20visited%20her%20sister%2C%20Patalamma%2C%20who%20had%20a%20hundred%20and%20one%20children%2C%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20village.%20She%20wanted%20to%20ask%20her%20to%20let%20her%20adopt%20one%20of%20her%20children.%20On%20learning%20of%20her%20sister%E2%80%99s%20intentions%2C%20Patalamma%20hid%20all%20her%20children.%20One%20of%20her%20children%2C%20Sidiranna%2C%20though%2C%20was%20seen%20playing%20outside.%20Taking%20this%20child%20with%20her%2C%20Madduramma%20turned%20all%20the%20hidden%C2%A0children%20into%20stone.%20The%20villagers%20still%20worship%20the%20stone%20idols%20of%20these%20children.%20Sidiranna%20visits%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20village%20to%20offer%20respects%C2%A0to%20his%20mother%20first%20before%20doing%20so%20for%20his%20foster%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeities%20of%20different%20castes%20can%20be%20related%20too.%20For%20instance%2C%20Kalamma%20is%20a%20deity%20of%20the%20craftsmen%2C%20Banashankariamma%20of%20the%20weavers%2C%20Hattimaramma%20of%20the%20Dalits%3A%20they%20are%20all%20sisters.%20Anjaneya%20is%20their%20brother%20in%20a%20few%20villages.%20Upper%20castes%20consider%20him%20their%20deity%20in%20some%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20festivals%2C%20the%20deities%20weep%20when%20their%20brothers%20or%20sisters%20do%20not%20arrive%20in%20time.%20Until%20the%20arrival%20of%20her%20sister%2C%20Beechnalliamma%2C%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20village%2C%20Haleooramma%20does%20not%20take%20a%20step%20at%20her%20festival.%20Festivals%20are%20sometimes%20organized%20to%20let%20sister%20deities%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAffection%2C%20love%2C%20and%20large-heartedness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Siddalingaiah%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9Care%20the%20primary%20qualities%20of%20village%20deities.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20festivals%20of%20village%20deities%2C%C2%A0different%20castes%20come%20together%20to%20celebrate%20it%20as%20a%20community%20festival.%C2%A0The%20central%20thought%20behind%20these%20festivals%20is%20the%20well-being%20of%20all.%C2%A0And%2C%20he%20added%2C%20there%20is%20the%20celebration%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20festivals%20of%20village%20deities%20celebrate%20the%20grandness%20of%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUrban%20migrants%20in%20cities%20usually%20visit%20their%20villages%20for%20the%20festival%20of%20their%20deities.%20In%20cases%20where%20migrant%20families%20from%20the%20same%20village%20live%20in%20the%20same%20neighbourhood%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20they%20arrange%20for%20their%20village%20deity%20to%20visit%20them%20in%20their%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20accounts%20of%20folk%20religion%20that%20he%20gathered%20for%20the%20monthly%20magazine%20of%20%3Cem%3ESamudaya%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20influential%20left%20theatre%20movement%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20in%20the%20early%20eighties%2C%20which%20were%20published%20later%20as%20%3Cem%3EAvataragalu%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Incarnations%2C%201982)%2C%20Siddalingaiah%20sought%20to%20demystify%20local%20religious%20practices.%20In%20Gulbarga%20district%2C%20young%20women%20freely%20abuse%20a%20male%20deity%20called%20Kui%20once%20a%20year.%20And%2C%20in%20Bidar%2C%20women%20line%20up%20to%20thrash%20a%20male%20deity%20called%20Nathuram%20with%20chappals.%20Both%20of%20these%20deities%2C%20Siddalingaiah%20explained%2C%20were%20known%20to%20have%20lusted%20after%20the%20wives%20of%20other%20men%20and%20now%20live%20in%20fear%20of%20their%20devotees.%20Making%20the%20gods%20a%20part%20of%20the%20social%20world%20and%20denying%20them%20their%20divine%20status%20is%20another%20of%20his%20logical%20attempts%20at%20unmasking%20religious%20life%20as%20a%20worldly%20affair%2C%20as%20a%20social%20delusion.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20Siddalingaiah%20noted%2C%20it%20was%20common%20to%20see%20gold%20coins%20falling%20out%20of%20Lakshmi%E2%80%99s%20hands.%20In%20recent%20times%2C%20rupee%20notes%20have%20taken%20the%20place%20of%20the%20gold%20coins.%20If%20the%20coins%20and%20rupees%20are%20phased%20out%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20he%20writes%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20cheque%20books%20will%20fall%20out%20of%20the%20Goddess%E2%80%99%20hands.%20Again%3A%20Gods%20address%20the%20lower-class%20individuals%20in%20the%20singular%2C%20and%20the%20rich%20with%20terms%20of%20respect.%20This%20sort%20of%20conduct%2C%20Siddalingaiah%20wrote%2C%20is%20seen%20in%20police%20stations.%20What%20then%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20police%20and%20our%20Gods%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFolk%20religious%20practices%20left%20Siddalingaiah%20puzzled%20at%20times.%20After%20possessing%20a%20devotee%2C%20a%20deity%20called%20Doddaswamy%20would%20start%20whistling%20with%20his%20fingers%20in%20his%20mouth.%20His%20devotees%20are%20expected%20to%20address%20him%20only%20through%20whistles.%20Another%20deity%20from%20Gulbarga%20district%2C%C2%A0Gajalakshmi%2C%20expected%20her%20devotees%20to%20bare%20all%20their%20teeth%20in%20her%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20translated%20below%2C%20in%20shortened%20form%2C%20a%20few%20of%20my%20favourite%20accounts%20of%20village%20deities%20found%20in%20Siddalingaiah%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EAvataragalu%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Aradavalli%20village%2C%20a%20devotee%20was%20greatly%20disappointed%20that%20his%20God%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20granted%20his%20wishes.%20His%20disappointment%20soon%20turned%20into%20anger.%20Grounding%20dried%20chillies%20into%20a%20powder%2C%20he%20made%20his%20way%20to%20the%20deity%E2%80%99s%20temple.%20%E2%80%9CGod%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20resolved%20my%20problems.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20make%20him%20suffer%20now.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20rub%20chilli%20powder%20on%20his%20body.%E2%80%9D%20He%20threatened%20those%20who%20tried%20to%20dissuade%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20rub%20this%20on%20your%20faces%20if%20you%20try%20to%20stop%20me.%E2%80%9D%20His%20resolve%20pained%20many%20of%20the%20devotees.%20While%20a%20few%20became%20curious%20about%20what%20might%20transpire%2C%20a%20few%20others%20could%20barely%20hold%20back%20their%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20reaching%20the%20temple%2C%20the%20aggrieved%20devotee%20stepped%20inside%20and%20began%20to%20rub%20the%20chilli%20powder%20all%20over%20the%20deity%E2%80%99s%20idol.%20Within%20moments%2C%20someone%20outside%20started%20howling%20in%20pain.%20The%20frightened%C2%A0devotees%20soon%20realized%20that%20the%20deity%20had%20possessed%20one%20among%20them.%20They%20held%20him%20tightly%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20are%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%3A%20%E2%80%9CMe%3F!%20I%E2%80%99m%20the%20God%20who%20is%20being%20attacked%20with%20chilli%20powder.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20do%20you%20want%20from%20us%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%3A%20%E2%80%9CStop%20putting%20chilli%20powder%20on%20me!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20hurts%20a%20lot!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAggrieved%20Devotee%20(AD)%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20said%20you%20would%20help%20me.%20Why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20keep%20your%20word%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%3A%20%E2%80%9CStop%20hurting%20me%20first.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20take%20care%20of%20your%20problem%20later.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAD%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20lying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20God.%20I%20never%20lie.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAD%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20you!%20I%E2%80%99ll%20put%20some%20more%20chilli%20powder%20on%20you.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20bear%20this%20pain%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAD%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ll%20give%20you%20one%20more%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGod%3A%20%E2%80%9CGuaranteed!%20Stop%20rubbing%20the%20chilli%20powder!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20possessed%20spirit%20slowly%20took%20leave.%20Everyone%20made%20their%20way%20home%20with%20much%20joy%20and%20relief.%20The%20discovery%20of%20a%20new%20way%20of%20having%C2%A0their%20wishes%20fulfilled%20also%20filled%20them%20with%20a%20secret%20delight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Dalit%20neighbourhood%20in%20Bengaluru%20had%20once%20organized%20a%20ceremony%20for%20Goddess%20Annamma%20from%20the%20Majestic%20area.%20Revered%20and%20feared%20by%20her%20devotees%2C%20she%20was%20often%20invited%20by%20various%20neighbourhoods.%20It%20cost%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20to%20have%20her%20visit%20from%20her%20temple%20in%20Majestic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20evening%20was%20grand%20and%20festive.%20The%20entire%20neighbourhood%20was%20decked%20up%20for%20the%20ceremonious%20occasion.%20Every%20household%20was%20filled%20with%20joy.%20The%20devotees%20surrounded%20the%20goddess%20with%20lamps.%20While%20the%20stately%20goddess%20sat%20under%20a%20pandal%20on%20the%20main%20road%2C%20everyone%20was%20scurrying%20around%2C%20attending%20to%20some%20task%20or%20another.%20Hundreds%20of%C2%A0people%20partook%20of%20the%20ceremony%20that%20began%20at%20ten%20in%20the%20night.%20The%20celebrations%20continued%20all%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20four%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20a%20man%20was%20seen%20rushing%20towards%20the%C2%A0deity.%20His%20eyes%20were%20wild.%20He%20was%20gnashing%20his%20teeth.%20The%20devotees%20somehow%20managed%20to%20hold%20him%20back.%20It%20soon%20became%20clear%20that%20another%20deity%2C%20Village%20Annamma%2C%20had%20possessed%20him.%20He%20then%20ran%20towards%20the%20Kabaddi%20ground%20opposite%20the%20main%20road.%20The%20others%20followed%20him%20as%20he%20led%20them%20to%20a%20small%20shrine%20in%20a%20corner%20of%20this%20ground.%20It%20had%20been%20built%20with%20four%20small%20stone%20slabs.%20A%20small%20stone%20planted%20on%20the%20ground%20inside%20this%20shrine%20was%20the%20idol%20of%20Village%20Annamma%20(VA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVillage%20Annamma%3A%20%E2%80%9CFools!%20Have%20you%20forgotten%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t!%20Can%20we%20ever%20forget%20you%3F%E2%80%9D%20VA%3A%20%E2%80%9CYou%20haven%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20me%20in%20so%20long.%20And%20now%2C%20all%20this%20special%C2%A0attention%20on%20the%20bitch%20from%20Majestic!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%3A%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20forgive%20our%20mistake%2C%20mother.%20We%20will%20give%20you%20your%20due%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVA%3A%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20I%20see%20how%20you%20are%20paying%20your%20due%20to%20me%3F%20I%E2%80%99ll%20show%20you%20what%20I%20can%20do!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotees%3A%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20don%E2%80%99t%20punish%20us.%20We%20are%20your%20children%2C%20all%20said%20and%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20devotees%20quickly%20set%20about%20tidying%20her%20shrine.%20They%20offered%20her%20a%20cock%20in%20sacrifice.%20The%20Goddess%20was%20placated%20somewhat%20at%20their%C2%A0response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20time%2C%20Majestic%20Annamma%20possessed%20a%20devotee.%20She%20rushed%20towards%20Village%20Annamma%E2%80%99s%20shrine%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20city%20deity.%20All%20the%20village%C2%A0deities%20should%20be%20under%20my%20control.%20Who%20is%20that%20speaking%20against%20me%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20devotees%20were%20bewildered.%20Restraining%20Majestic%20Annamma%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20scuffle%20between%20the%20two%20deities%20followed.%20A%20little%20later%2C%20the%20person%20whom%20Village%20Annamma%20had%20possessed%20was%20found%20with%20his%20teeth%20broken%C2%A0and%20the%20one%20possessed%20by%20Majestic%20Annamma%20was%20in%20tattered%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Srirampura%2C%20God%20Muneshwara%20possessed%20a%20man%20regularly.%20He%20had%20numerous%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20elderly%20devotee%20would%20visit%20him%20every%20week%20to%20seek%20his%20help%20to%C2%A0rid%20his%20son%20of%20difficulty.%20Before%20taking%20leave%2C%20he%20would%20give%20two%20rupees%20as%20a%20token%20offering.%20One%20day%2C%20the%20deity%20became%20furious%2C%20%E2%80%9CTwo%20rupees%20won%E2%80%99t%20do!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotee%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20this%3F%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20offered%20you%20two%20rupees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeity%3A%20%E2%80%9CDirty%20fellow!%20I%E2%80%99ve%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20bigger%20offering.%20Put%20down%20three%20rupees%20at%20least.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotee%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20raise%20it%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeity%20(roared)%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20raise%20it%3F!%20Any%20idea%20how%20much%20a%20kg%20of%20rice%20costs%3F%20Do%20you%20know%20the%20cost%20of%20kerosene%20these%20days%3F%20Even%20a%20cinema%20ticket%20costs%20a%20lot%20now.%20If%20you%20only%20offer%20two%20rupees%2C%20how%20can%20I%20lead%20my%20life%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevotee%20(searching%20his%20pockets)%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20see%20your%20point%2C%20my%20Lord.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKariyamma%2C%20a%20deity%20in%20Chikmagalur%2C%20asked%20her%20devotees%20for%20a%20pen%C2%A0and%20some%20paper.%20She%20wanted%20to%20write%20a%20letter%20to%20her%20elder%20brother%2C%20Lord%20Manjunatha%20at%20Dharmasthala.%20The%20devotees%20never%20knew%20that%20the%C2%A0deity%20had%20a%20brother.%20She%20hit%20back%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20had%20you%20thought%20of%20me%3F%20I%E2%80%99ve%20relatives%20all%20over.%20Even%20in%20far%20off%20places%20like%20Bengaluru%20and%20Bombay.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deity%20made%20a%20series%20of%20scratch%20marks%20on%20the%20paper.%20She%20would%C2%A0pause%20to%20think%20before%20making%20each%20one%20of%20those%20marks.%20After%20the%20letter%20was%20done%2C%20it%20was%20mailed%20to%20Lord%20Manjunatha%20at%20Dharmasthala.%20The%20devotees%20were%20delighted%20to%20see%20a%20letter%20passing%20between%20Gods.%20A%20reply%20from%20Dharmasthala%20arrived%20two%20weeks%20later.%20The%20deity%20was%20jubilant.%20Everyone%20gathered%20to%20read%20the%20letter.%20The%20reply%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20brief%3A%20%E2%80%9CPlease%20send%20a%20letter%20only%20if%20you%20can%20write%20in%20Kannada.%20Do%20not%20send%C2%A0meaningless%20scratch%20marks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deity%20had%20wished%20to%20brag%20that%20she%20was%20literate.%20After%20this%20episode%2C%20she%20kept%20out%20of%20letter%20writing%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENever%20high-decibel%2C%20and%20always%20gentle%2C%20affectionate%20and%20witty%2C%20Siddalingaiah%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20of%20folk%20religion%20end%20up%20being%20a%20moving%20experience%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%20Since%20his%20early%20writings%20on%20village%20goddesses%2C%20he%20came%20to%20show%20less%20interest%20in%20viewing%20religion%20as%20a%20cover%20for%20social%20games%20and%20care%20more%20for%20the%20deeper%20meanings%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20I%20did%20with%20him%20several%20years%20ago%2C%20Siddalingaiah%C2%A0explained%3A%20%E2%80%9CMockery%20was%20central%20to%20%3Cem%3EAvataragalu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Because%20of%20my%20rationalist%20background%2C%20I%20used%20to%20make%20fun%20of%20gods%20for%20a%20few%20years.%20But%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20like%20that%20anymore.%20For%20example%2C%20people%20suddenly%20start%20lashing%20themselves%20with%20a%20whip.%20I%20would%20have%20probably%20made%20fun%20of%20this%20earlier.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20look%20at%20it%20differently%20now.%20This%20person%20is%20inflicting%20self-violence%20(%3Cem%3Esva-himse%3C%2Fem%3E).%20Why%20is%20he%20doing%20this%3F%20What%20are%20its%20origins%3F%20I%20would%20ask%20such%20questions%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20extract%20from%20a%20chapter%20of%20the%20book%3C%2Fem%3E%20Another%20India%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eby%20Chandan%20Gowda.%20The%20chapter%20is%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20World%20of%20Village%20Deities%E2%80%99.%20The%20extract%20has%20been%20published%20with%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20permission.%20The%20book%20will%20be%20released%20on%20September%2012.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694427621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11154223%2Fimage-1312.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-extract-the-world-of-village-deities-in-karnataka-another-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20goddess%20once%20discouraged%20her%20devotees%20from%20building%20a%20shrine%20for%20her.%20She%20wanted%20to%20be%20left%20free%20to%20wander%20as%20she%20pleased%20whereas%20the%20shrine%20door%20would%20restrict%20her%20movements.%20The%20doorless%20shrine%20her%20devotees%20then%20built%20for%20her%20still%20exists%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Bengaluru.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20the%20'G'%20of%20G20%2C%20The%20Long%20Shadow%20of%20Gandhi%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11153247%2FUntitled-design-2-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20only%20family%20photo-op%20of%20the%20G20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fg-20-declaration-as-the-west-scrambles-to-justify-its-softening-stance-on-moscow-russia-exults%5C%22%3Ethat%20was%20possible%20was%20at%20Rajghat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20place%20where%20the%20Mahatma%20was%20laid%20to%20rest%20after%20his%20assassination%20by%20Nathuram%20Godse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWestern%20leaders%20at%20the%20G20%20have%20refused%20the%20family%20photo%20involving%20any%20Russians%2C%20but%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20strong%20imprint%20on%20the%20world%20stage%20and%20his%20deep%20impression%20as%20the%20best%20thing%20India%20can%20present%20about%20itself%20to%20the%20world%20came%20through%20as%20the%20next%20President%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20the%20Brazilian%20President%2C%20Lula%20D%E2%80%99%20Silva%2C%20made%20it%20clear%20how%20emotional%20he%20got%20when%20he%20went%20to%20the%20Mahatma%E2%80%99s%20memorial%2C%20referring%20to%20him%20as%20%E2%80%9Cdear%20Gandhi.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdear-gandhi-brazilian-president-lula-touched-after-raj-ghat-visit-101694337096529.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELula%20told%20the%20media%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEverybody%20knows%20that%20in%20my%20political%20life%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20has%20great%20meaning%20because%20the%20struggle%20with%20non-violence%20was%20a%20role%20model%20that%20I%20followed%20for%20many%20decades%20when%20I%20was%20in%20the%20Labour%20Movement.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20am%20very%20much%20touched%20and%20emotional%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20and%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20have%20a%20grave%20Mahatma%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20one%20which%20has%20often%20meant%20invoking%20Gandhi%20abroad%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Funion-minister-giriraj-singh-says-godse-a-saput-of-india%5C%22%3Ehis%20assassin%20Nathuram%20Godse%20when%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20came%20into%20sharp%20focus%20when%20the%20G20%20was%20held.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20flag-bearers%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Finternational%2Farchive%2F2022%2F06%2Fgodse-cult-gandhi-assassin-india%2F661154%2F%5C%22%3Eideology%20that%20assassinated%20him%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20how%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fncert-deletions-about-gandhis-assassination-show-how-shrewdly-the-operation-was-planned%5C%22%3Econstantly%20discredit%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20yet%20extract%20it%20and%20use%20it%20for%20the%20propagation%20of%20an%20idea%20of%20Gandhi-land%20is%20a%20dilemma%20that%20refuses%20to%20go%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20posted%20this%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20ideals%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20reverberate%20globally.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJ4Ko3IXpe4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJ4Ko3IXpe4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1700803436789571807%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2010%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20would%20be%20a%20routine%20thing%20coming%20from%20any%20other%20Indian%20prime%20minister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20a%20series%20of%20attempts%20have%20been%20made%20in%20the%20recent%20past%20to%20further%20take%20away%20and%20insult%20the%20Gandhian%20legacy%20of%20non-violence%20and%20composite%20Indian%20nationalism%2C%20going%20as%20far%20as%20to%20deify%20his%20assassin%20Godse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A2%20This%20October%202%2C%20it%20is%20believed%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fgandhis-great-grandson-moves-sc-challenging-sabarmati-ashram-redevelopment%5C%22%3Etakeover%20of%20Sabarmati%20Ashram%20will%20be%20complete%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Modi%20present%20at%20the%20spot.%20Beyond%20the%20architectural%20reworking%20of%20the%20historical%20space%2C%20through%20a%20project%20criticised%20consistently%20by%20Gandhians%2C%20autonomous%20institutions%20passing%20directly%20into%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20control%20make%20the%20takeover%20complete.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Other%20Gandhian%20institutions%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-varanasi-occupants-of-iconic-gandhian-institution-thrown-out-their-land-taken-over%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20Varanasi%20for%20example%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20saw%20%E2%80%9Coccupants%20of%20an%20iconic%20Gandhian%20institution%20thrown%20out%20and%20land%20taken%20over%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20July.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A2%20Meanwhile%2C%20Gita%20Press%20was%20given%20the%20Gandhi%20Peace%20Prize%2C%202021.%20But%20as%20Akshaya%20Mukul%E2%80%99s%20biography%20of%20the%20Gita%20Press%20outlines%2C%20the%20award%20was%20a%20way%20of%20trying%20to%20both%20distort%20and%20appropriate%20Gandhi%2C%20because%20the%20Gita%20Press%20was%20the%20biggest%20critic%20of%20Gandhian%20thought%20in%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20lifetime.%20They%20did%20not%20even%20refer%20to%20his%20assassination%20for%20months%20and%20their%20top%20people%20were%20amongst%20those%20arrested%20after%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20and%20RSS%20associates%20were%20being%20picked%20up%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20killing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fmahatma-gandhi-gita-press%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMukul%20writes%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%20Gita%20Press%E2%80%99%20flagship%20magazine%5D%20Kalyan%E2%80%99s%20virulent%20attack%20on%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20to%20cause%20Poddar%20considerable%20trouble%20five%20months%20after%20Independence.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination%20on%2030%20January%201948%20in%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Birla%20House%20by%20Nathuram%20Godse%20and%20others%20associated%20with%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20and%20RSS%2C%20resulted%20in%20the%20arrest%20of%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20people%20throughout%20the%20country%E2%80%94among%20them%20Poddar%20and%20his%20mentor%20Jaydayal%20Goyandka.%20G.D.%20Birla%20refused%20to%20help%20the%20two%2C%20and%20even%20protested%20when%20Sir%20Badridas%20Goenka%20took%20up%20their%20case.%20For%20Birla%2C%20the%20two%20were%20not%20propagating%20sanatan%20dharma%20but%20shaitan%20(evil)%20dharma.%20Strangely%2C%20the%20rich%20private%20archives%20in%20Gorakhpur%20contain%20no%20reference%20to%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20assassination.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%A2%20Gandhi%20being%20diminished%20with%20reference%20to%20the%20Khadi%20in%20the%20Khadi%20and%20Village%20Industries%20Commission%20calendar%20made%20news%20in%202017.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20deletes%20Gandhi%20from%20Khadi%20Gram%20Udyog%20calendars%3A%20No%20KVIC%20rules%20on%20photos%2C%20says%20government%E2%80%9D%2C%20read%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fnarendra-modi-mahatma-gandhi-khadi-gram-udyog-charkha-954810-2017-01-13%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%20news%20report%20on%20January%2013%2C%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20PMO%20sources%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndia%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EToday%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Ctermed%20the%20Khadi%20controversy%20an%20%E2%80%98unnecessary%E2%80%99%20one%20citing%20years%20from%20the%20past%2C%20when%20the%20KVIC%20calendars%20did%20not%20have%20the%20photographs%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20G20%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3EGandhi%20seemed%20to%20have%20disappeared%20completely%20from%20the%20spinning%20section%20in%20the%20Crafts%20Bazar%20at%20Bharat%20Mandapam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11151801%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-3.17.54-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221192%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11151801%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-3.17.54-PM.png%201192w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11151801%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-3.17.54-PM-300x168.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11151801%2FScreenshot-2023-09-11-at-3.17.54-PM-1024x574.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-672536%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%