Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPathaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20year.%20The%20reasons%20were%20many%20%E2%80%93%20he%20was%20back%20on%20the%20big%20screen%20after%20ages%20and%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20defy%20the%20haters.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20dragged%20my%20teenage%20son%20and%20tween%20daughter.%20My%20children%20were%20not%20impressed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EExcept%20for%20the%20three%20very%20important%20things%20%E2%80%93%20SRK%E2%80%99s%20good%20looks%2C%20good%20looks%20and%20good%20looks%2C%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20anything%20for%20me%20in%20the%20movie.%20I%20did%20understand%20the%20hype%2C%20I%20felt%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPathaan%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20success%20was%20because%20of%20the%20hand%20of%20divine%2C%20a%20triumph%20for%20love%20in%20the%20times%20of%20hate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESRK%20has%20given%20us%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDear%20Zindagi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESwades%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EChak%20De%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERaees%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Or%20romances%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDilwale%20Dulhaniya%20Le%20Jayenge%2C%20Kabhi%20Khushi%20Kabhi%20Gham%2C%20Kuch%20Kuch%20Hota%20Hai%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDilwale%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20where%20he%20opened%20his%20arms%20and%20jumped%20right%20into%20our%20hearts.%20I%20am%20saying%20in%20the%20lowest%20possible%20decibel%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20movie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20me%2C%20a%20few%20smiles%2C%20the%20flashing%20of%20the%20dimples%2C%20the%20subtle%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eadabs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(greetings)%20and%20some%20nice%20songs%20were%20%3Cem%3Ep%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaisa%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ev%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Easool%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(worth%20the%20money).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20loved%20the%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20movie%20hall%2C%20I%20liked%20the%20fact%20that%20people%20were%20making%20a%20statement.%20They%20had%20come%20for%20love%20and%20were%20defying%20and%20denouncing%20hate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20liked%20that%20SRK%20had%20not%20followed%20the%20much%20in-vogue%20norm%20of%20%E2%80%98making%20villains%20of%20a%20community%20and%20a%C2%A0%20neighbouring%20country%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20selling%20formula.%20Even%20if%20Pakistan%20was%20the%20villain%2C%20it%20was%20not%20the%20people%2C%20just%20a%20few%20rogue%20generals.%20Except%20for%20the%20reference%20to%20Article%20370%20%2C%20which%20for%20me%20as%20a%20Kashmiri%20is%20still%20contentious%2C%20I%20found%20the%20movie%20much%20saner%20than%20some%20of%20the%20recent%20hits.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20of%20course%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20quench%20my%20thirst%20for%20an%20SRK%20movie.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20when%20people%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20going%20for%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sure%20I%20would.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20no%20haters%20to%20prove%20wrong%20this%20time.%20The%20posters%20spoke%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edishum%20dishum%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(action)%20as%20the%20genre%20and%20honestly%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20the%20bandaged%20or%20the%20bald%20look%20of%20SRK.%20For%20me%2C%20he%20is%20the%20suave%20and%20sexy%20NRI%2C%20wearing%20the%20%E2%80%98cool%E2%80%99%20chain%20on%20his%20fluorescent%20hoodies.%20I%20was%20okay%20waiting%20for%20its%20OTT%20release.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20release%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20my%20plans.%20The%20movie%20reviews%20told%20me%20it%20is%20an%20answer%20to%20all%20my%20grudges%20and%20disappointments%20I%20had%20as%20a%20fan%2C%20despite%20my%20unflinching%20love%20for%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20always%20wanted%20SRK%20to%20be%20like%20Meryl%20Streep%20but%20he%20refused%20and%20even%20said%20our%20expectations%20were%20unfounded.%20He%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Che%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20the%20situation%20enough%20so%20he%20would%20want%20to%20keep%20quiet%20and%20not%20add%20to%20the%20noise%E2%80%9D.%20I%20wanted%20to%20tell%20him%20that%20his%20words%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20noise%2C%20it%20would%20be%20power.%20I%20wanted%20to%20tell%20him%20that%20journalists%20might%20not%20be%20the%20same%20as%20they%20were%20years%20ago%2C%20but%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20forgo%20our%20responsibility%20as%20a%20citizen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20be%20like%20Robert%20De%20Niro%2C%20not%20that%20I%20wanted%20him%20to%20call%20someone%20%E2%80%9Cstupid%E2%80%9D.%20I%20surely%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20him%20to%20waste%20a%20priceless%20answer%20and%20talk%20about%20the%20then%20US%20president%20to%20David%20Letterman%20while%20choosing%20to%20remain%20mum%20about%20his%20own%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20looked%20for%20a%20tweet%20after%20every%20rape%2C%20every%20lynching%2C%20every%20hate%20crime%2C%20every%20lopsided%20judgement%2C%20every%20attack%20on%20students%2C%20but%20there%20was%20nothing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20however%2C%20I%20did%20realise%20that%20his%20silence%20was%20better.%20Except%20for%20a%20few%20selfies%2C%20he%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20done%20much%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20side%20of%20power.%20I%20had%20realised%2C%20or%20maybe%20wanted%20to%20believe%2C%20that%20his%20silence%20was%20his%20protest.%20As%20a%20Kashmiri%2C%20I%20have%20understood%20the%20meaning%20of%20silences%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Maybe%20my%20silence%20let%20me%20empathise%20with%20his.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20while%20I%2C%20like%20millions%20of%20his%20other%20fans%2C%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20the%20movie%20theatre%20just%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPathaan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20released%2C%20the%20superstar%20did%20not%20outrightly%20want%20to%20make%20one.%20In%20the%20famous%20Kolkata%20event%20he%20did%20talk%20about%20the%20toxicity%20of%20social%20media%20and%20said%20%E2%80%98how%20positive%20people%20are%20sitting%20alive%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20message%20just%20fell%20a%20little%20short.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJawan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20SRK%20seems%20to%20have%20finally%20realised%20that%20after%20his%20fans%2C%20it%20is%20his%20turn%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20and%20that%20too%20a%20big%20one.%20Whether%20it%20was%20his%20son%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20or%20whether%20he%20realised%20that%20no%20matter%20how%20quiet%20he%20remained%2C%20those%20who%20wanted%20to%20question%20his%20nationalism%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOr%20maybe%20because%20he%20realised%20that%20whatever%20he%20does%2C%20his%20name%20is%20Khan%20and%20he%20might%20not%20be%20a%20terrorist%20but%20he%20will%20always%20be%20questioned.%20Perhaps%C2%A0%20he%20simply%20found%20his%20voice%20because%20so%20many%20others%20had%20become%20voiceless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20he%20has%20done%20it%20and%20how.%20The%20monologue%20in%20the%20climax%20of%20%3Cem%3EJawan%3C%2Fem%3E%20gave%20me%20goosebumps.%20Shahrukh%20has%20spoken%20and%20at%20the%20correct%20platform.%20He%20has%20spoken%20through%20his%20art%20and%20his%20platform%20is%20the%2070%20feet%20screen%20with%20hundreds%20of%20people%20watching%2C%20with%20no%20jingoistic%20anchors%20there%20to%20label%20him%20anti-national%20and%20no%20unruly%20politician%20asking%20him%20to%20go%20to%20Pakistan.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20he%20talks%20about%20democracy%20and%20the%20power%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20he%20tells%20you%20to%20question%20those%20who%20want%20to%20rule%20you%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20When%20he%20says%20to%20ask%20them%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etum%20mere%20liye%20kya%20karoge%20(what%20will%20you%20do%20for%20me)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20he%20is%20throwing%20an%20open%20challenge%2C%20not%20just%20to%20those%20who%20want%20votes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20caste%2C%20creed%20and%20religion%2C%20but%20also%20to%20those%20who%20claim%20otherwise%20and%20end%20up%20agreeing%20to%20the%20same%20politics%20as%20%E2%80%98that%20is%20the%20pulse%20of%20the%20people%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20wants%20you%20to%20think%20about%20it%20when%20you%20leave%20the%20theatre%20and%20are%20driving%20home%20with%20your%20family.%20He%20wants%20you%20to%20ask%20the%20politicians%20what%20they%20will%20do%20to%20bridge%20the%20divide%20which%20has%20been%20driving%20a%20wedge%20between%20communities%20for%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20wants%20you%20to%20ask%20if%20the%20names%20of%20gods%20will%20still%20be%20used%20as%20a%20war%20cry%20against%20a%20community.%20What%20will%20you%20do%20to%20make%20sure%20clothes%20don%E2%80%99t%20define%20a%20person%20and%20identity%20is%20beyond%20the%20length%20of%20a%20beard%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20will%20they%20do%20to%20make%20sure%20a%20boycott%20call%20of%20communities%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20become%20a%20letter%20officially%20submitted%20to%20a%20police%20station%3F%20He%20wants%20you%20to%20ask%20them%2C%20how%20will%20they%20ensure%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20stay%20on%20roads%20to%20be%20heard%3F%20He%20wants%20you%20to%20ask%20them%20how%20they%20will%20ensure%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20find%20bodies%20floating%20around%20Ganga%20ghats%20if%20another%20pandemic%20hits%20us.%20He%20wants%20you%20to%20ask%20them%20what%20they%20will%20do%20to%20ensure%20Olympic%20medalists%20are%20not%20dragged%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20not%20belittle%20his%20message%20by%20saying%20when%20he%20lifts%20his%20hand%2C%20he%20is%20asking%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20party%20with%20that%20symbol.%20The%20message%20is%20as%20much%20for%20that%20party%20as%20it%20is%20for%20anyone%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20someone%20praised%20the%20monologue%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20give%20spoilers%20by%20talking%20about%20the%20contents.%20But%20SRK%20insisted%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDesh%20ki%20bhalaai%20ke%20liye%20sab%20spoilers%20maaf%20(If%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20the%20wellbeing%20of%20the%20country%2C%20spoilers%20are%20allowed)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Everyone%20should%20exercise%20their%20right%20to%20vote%20intelligently%20and%20responsibly%E2%80%99%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESRK%2C%20I%20hear%20you.%20And%20so%20does%20everyone%20else.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EToufiq%20Rashid%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20covered%20the%20Kashmir%20conflict%2C%20health%20and%20wellbeing%20for%20top%20Indian%20newspapers%20for%20nearly%20two%20decades.%20She%20now%20works%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pixstory.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%40Pixstory%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694426366000%2C%22visual%22%