r%20its%20Ghosi%20By-Poll%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11143642%2FF5mLR8eb0AAaZcJ.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20victory%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20Ghosi%20has%20generated%20excitement%20among%20the%20constituents%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20particularly%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20observers%20believe%20that%20the%20victory%20might%20be%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20annals%20as%20Mohsina%20Kidwai%E2%80%99s%20win%20of%20the%20Azamgarh%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20the%201978%20by-election%20had%20been%2C%20following%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%201977%20general%20elections.%20It%20had%20revived%20the%20fortune%20of%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20in%20north%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20lost%20massively%20to%20the%20Janata%20Party%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20among%20other%20north%20Indian%20states%20and%20had%20lost%20power%20at%20the%20Union%20government%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20Independence%20in%201977.%20Mohsina%20Kidwai%E2%80%99s%20victory%20heralded%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20recovery.%20It%20eventually%20came%20back%20to%20power%20in%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victory%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Sudharkar%20Singh%20against%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20candidate%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20by%2042%2C759%20votes%20in%20a%20constituency%20that%20is%20said%20to%20have%20over%2060%2C000%20Dalit%20voters%20is%20quite%20stupendous.%20Chauhan%20is%20noted%20as%20a%20frequent%20switcher%20of%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20close%20look%20at%20the%20political%20realities%20of%201978%20and%20the%20situation%2045%20years%20down%20the%20line%20in%202023%20suggests%20that%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20the%20most%20active%20INDIA%20coalition%20members%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20will%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go%20to%20defeat%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20heartland%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fus-president-biden-says-he-raised-importance-of-human-rights-and-free-press-with-pm-modi%5C%22%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20Is%20INDIA-1%20and%20NDA-0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20secured%2032.1%25%20votes%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2041.29%25%20in%20the%202022%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20Congress%20had%20secured%20barely%202.33%25%20votes%20%E2%80%93%20by%20all%20accounts%20an%20insignificant%20vote-share%20in%20the%20most%20populous%20state.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20vote-share%20had%20gone%20sharply%20up%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%202017%20elections%20when%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20outfit%20had%20secured%20only%2021.8%25%20votes%20and%20had%20been%20reduced%20to%2047%20seats.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20seats%20also%20went%20up%20to%20111.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20vote-share%20remained%20almost%20the%20same%20in%202017%20and%202022%20but%20its%20seats%20got%20reduced%20substantially.%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20party%20bagged%20255%20seats%20in%202022%2C%20against%20312%20in%202017.%20Thus%2C%20the%20combined%20vote-shares%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20too%20would%20not%20have%20made%20any%20difference%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202022%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVulnerability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20the%20Ghosi%20by-poll%20results%20have%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20small%20caste-based%20parties%20which%20have%20been%20operating%20in%20the%20sub-regions%20of%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20For%20example%2C%20leaders%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20and%20Omprakash%20Rajbhar%20who%20were%20believed%20to%20have%20had%20a%20sway%20over%20their%20respective%20castes%20of%20Nonia%20and%20Bhar%2C%20have%20ostensibly%20been%20losing%20significance%20in%20state%20politics.%20Both%20have%20recently%20late%20switched%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20after%20earlier%20associations%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20But%20they%20had%20hardly%20made%20a%20difference%20to%20the%20prospects%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20when%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20had%20brought%20them%20into%20its%20fold%20in%20the%202022%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20noticeable%20point%20is%20the%20increasingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmayawati-bsp-dalit-votes-india-nda%5C%22%3Edwindling%20clout%20of%20Mayawati%20and%20her%20Bahujan%20Samajwadi%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20party%20was%20reduced%20to%20a%20solitary%20seat%20and%20secured%20only%2012.88%25%20votes%20in%202022%20%E2%80%93%20an%20all-time%20low%20vote-share%20in%20the%20last%2030%20years.%20There%20was%20an%20allegation%20that%20Mayawati%20%C2%A0had%20helped%20the%20BJP%20against%20Samajwadi%20Party%20in%202022%20by%20%E2%80%9Ctransferring%E2%80%9D%20her%20non-Jatav%20Dalit%20votes%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%20and%20fielding%20more%20Muslim%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20extent%20to%20which%20Mayawati%20helped%20the%20BJP%20in%202022%20is%20subject%20to%20study.%20But%20Ghosi%20has%20offered%20verifiable%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20Dalit%20voters%20did%20not%20heed%20her%20call%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20voting%20at%20the%20by-polls.%20Despite%20Ghosi%20having%20a%20significant%20Dalit%20population%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20candidate%20secured%20about%2058%25%20votes%20against%20his%20rival%20at%20the%20seat%2C%20suggesting%20that%20it%20did%20secure%20the%20Dalit%20votes%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20exists%20a%20big%20chasm%20in%20the%20vote-shares%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20INDIA.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20image%20has%2C%20of%20course%2C%20improved%20since%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20and%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20massive%20victory%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20Karnataka%20results%20had%20also%20cast%20a%20doubt%20over%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20capability%20to%20win%20polls%20for%20his%20party%20for%20he%20was%20the%20main%20face%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20can%20ill-afford%20to%20be%20complacent%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20some%20recent%20positives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-bypoll-ghosi-dhupguri-kerala-tripura%5C%22%3EINDIA%20Alliance%20Passes%20First%20By-Poll%20Test%20Well%2C%20But%20Needs%20to%20Sort%20Out%20Differences%20in%20Key%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBihar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20striking%20similarities%20between%20the%20demographic%20behaviour%20of%20the%20people%20in%20western%20Bihar%20and%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20But%20chances%20are%20that%20INDIA%20would%20fare%20better%20in%20Bihar%2C%20not%20only%20in%20comparison%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20but%20to%20several%20other%20states%20including%20Haryana%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20comprising%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20had%20secured%2045.39%20%25%20votes%20including%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2023.58%25%20and%20the%20JD(U)%E2%80%99s%2021.81%25.%20The%20combine%20had%20won%2039%20seats%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20drawing%20a%20blank%20and%20the%20Congress%20winning%20the%20solitary%20Kishenganj%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20struggled%20to%20remain%20a%20potent%20force%20in%20the%20state%20every%20time%20the%20JD(U)%20lhas%20eft%20it%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal.%20The%202015%20assembly%20elections%20are%20a%20benchmark%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20and%20INDIA%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDU-RJD-Congress%20grand%20alliance%20had%20secured%2041.8%25%20votes%2C%20winning%20178%20seats%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2034.1%25%20and%2053%20seats%20in%20its%20share%20in%20the%20state%20in%202015.%20Now%2C%20the%20INDIA%20grouping%20has%20the%20CPI-ML-Liberation%2C%20which%20is%20the%20biggest%20Left%20party%20with%20a%20substantial%20vote-share%20in%20several%20pockets%20of%20central%2C%20south%20and%20north%20Bihar.%20But%20the%20BJP%20which%20has%20lost%20the%20JD(U)%20has%20made%20no%20additions%20in%20terms%20of%20allies%20with%20a%20meaningful%20support%20base%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20publicly%20effusive%20about%20getting%20the%20outfits%20of%20Upendra%20Kushwaha%2C%20a%20Koiri%20leader%20and%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20a%20Musahar%20leader%20in%20its%20fold.%20But%20Kushwaha%20and%20Manjhi%20were%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%202015%20elections%20too.%20It%20will%20be%20hardly%20surprising%20if%20Manjhi%E2%80%99s%20and%C2%A0%20Kushwaha%E2%80%99s%20parties%20meet%20the%20same%20fate%20that%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20and%20Omprakash%20Rajbhar%20have%20met%20in%20Ghosi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694424035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fghosi-india-uttar-pradesh-bjp-alliance-caste-vote%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20parties%20of%20the%20group%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(Congress%20and%20Samajwadi%20Party)%2C%20even%20with%20their%20combined%20strength%2C%20lag%20behind%20the%20BJP.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fghosi-india-uttar-pradesh-bjp-alliance-caste-vote%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20Is%20Rife%20With%20Stories%20of%20Sexual%20Harassment.%20What%20Is%20the%20BCCI%20Doing%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11141808%2FFo3NBAMagAEstBs.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20Sharda%20Ugra%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsports%2Fbjp-bcci-jay-shah%3Futm_source%3Dwire%26utm_medium%3Dexcerpt%26utm_campaign%3Dtest%5C%22%3Ecover%20story%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20The%20Caravan%2C%20on%20how%20the%20BCCI%20escapes%20regulatory%20scrutiny.%20Drunk%20on%20its%20wealth%20generated%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half%2C%20with%20the%20new%20muscle%20of%20its%20proximity%20to%20the%20BJP%20regime%2C%20the%20BCCI%20pays%20no%20attention%20to%20the%20acid%20in%20its%20groundwater.%20Read%20the%20full%20story%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsports%2Fbjp-bcci-jay-shah%3Futm_source%3Dwire%26utm_medium%3Dexcerpt%26utm_campaign%3Dtest%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20there%20is%20another%20%E2%80%9Csunrise%20sector%E2%80%9D%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20that%20is%20as%20full%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%20of%20shadows%20as%20BCCI%E2%80%99s%20state%20associations%2C%20it%20is%20Jay%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20cause%20c%C3%A9l%C3%A8bre%3A%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket.%20Following%20India%E2%80%99s%20final%20appearance%20in%20the%202017%20Women%E2%80%99s%20World%20Cup%2C%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20game%20has%20burst%20into%20wider%20public%20consciousness%2C%20and%20Shah%20wants%20to%20be%20seen%20as%20their%20torchbearer%20in%20the%20BCCI.%20In%20October%202022%2C%20within%20two%20weeks%20of%20being%20re-elected%20BCCI%20secretary%2C%20Shah%20announced%20equal%20match%20fees%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20international%20men%20and%20women%20cricketers.%20It%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Premier%20League%2C%20in%20March%2C%20in%20which%20BCCI%20offered%20salaries%20of%20the%20kind%20rarely%20seen%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20team%20sports%20worldwide.%20In%20a%20detailed%20interview%20given%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Shah%20said%20he%20believed%20the%20pay%20parity%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwatershed%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Indian%20cricket%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20WPL%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Csecond%20biggest%20cricket%20league%20in%20the%20world%20after%20IPL.%E2%80%9D%20Based%20on%20WPL%20numbers%E2%80%94Rs%20951%20crore%20for%20a%20five-year%20media%20rights%20deal%20and%20player%20salaries%20higher%20than%20the%2026-year-old%20WNBA%E2%80%94women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20became%20a%20sunrise%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stories%20outside%20the%20headline%20makers%20and%20their%20headline-making%20numbers%20are%20murky%20and%20frightening.%20This%20year%2C%20a%20special%20POCSO%20court%20in%20Dehradun%20heard%20a%20case%20against%2065-year-old%20Narendra%20Shah%2C%20the%20CAU%E2%80%99s%20co-convenor%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20and%20secretary%20of%20the%20Chamoli%20District%20Cricket%20Association.%20A%20teenager%20accused%20him%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20bullying%20and%20obscene%20phone%20calls.%20A%20conversation%20has%20been%20recorded.%20In%20the%20police%20complaint%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20complainant%2C%20who%20will%20turn%2016%20in%20September%2C%20said%20that%20Narendra%20Shah%20had%20been%20harassing%20her%20and%20touching%20her%20inappropriately%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20also%20accuses%20Narendra%20Shah%20of%20saying%20that%20the%20complainant%20would%20have%20to%20fulfil%20the%20physical%20needs%20of%20the%20CAU%20secretary%2C%20Mahim%20Verma%2C%20and%20the%20CAU%20member%20Dhiraj%20Bhandari%2C%20whose%20names%20he%20would%20often%20drop.%20It%20accuses%20Narendra%20of%20hurling%20casteist%20abuse%20towards%20the%20minor%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ETum%20log%20neech%20jati%20ke%20log%20ho%2C%20tumhe%20unchi%20jati%20ke%20logon%20ke%20saath%20rehne%20ka%20adhikar%20nahin%20hai%2C%20phir%20bhi%20main%20tumhe%20khila%20sakta%20hoon%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%E2%80%94You%20belong%20to%20a%20lower%20caste%20and%20do%20not%20have%20the%20right%20to%20live%20with%20upper-caste%20people%2C%20but%20still%20I%20will%20give%20you%20the%20opportunity%20to%20play.%20Narendra%20was%20arrested%20briefly%2C%20but%20the%20police%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20for%20his%20remand%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20the%20magistrate%2C%20with%20Narendra%20citing%20ill%20health%20and%20a%20suicide%20attempt.%20This%20ruling%20is%20now%20being%20challenged.%20Narendra%20has%20been%20summoned%20before%20the%20court%20and%20has%20also%20been%20charged%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%20Verma%2C%20while%20refusing%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20matter%20because%20the%20case%20was%20subjudice%2C%20stated%20%E2%80%9Cas%20soon%20as%20the%20matter%20came%20to%20light%2C%20the%20Apex%20Council%20of%20CAU%20removed%20Mr.%20Narendra%20Shah%20from%20his%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20referred%20to%20an%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20kind%20of%20wealth%20available%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20safeguards%2C%20there%20is%20no%20estimating%20what%20a%20more%20accurate%20number%20of%20cricketers%20facing%20harassment%20by%20their%20superiors%E2%80%94coaches%2C%20selectors%2C%20officials%E2%80%94may%20be.%20Women%20cricketers%20who%20have%20left%20the%20game%20are%20able%20to%20draw%20a%20clearer%20picture%2C%20but%20on%20condition%20of%20revealing%20neither%20their%20names%20nor%20the%20states%20they%20represented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20cricketer%20who%20represented%20her%20state%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20was%20forced%20out%20of%20cricket%20for%20ignoring%20a%20coach%20who%20sought%20sexual%20favours%20from%20her%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20spot%20in%20the%20playing%20eleven.%20The%20cricketer%20was%20picked%20for%20a%20series%2C%20told%20to%20prepare%20to%20play%20in%20a%20game%20the%20following%20day%20and%20then%20left%20out.%20This%20happened%20through%20the%20series%2C%20until%2C%20with%20one%20match%20to%20go%2C%20came%20the%20same%20instruction%E2%80%94be%20ready%20for%20tomorrow.%20At%2010%20pm%20the%20night%20before%20the%20last%20game%2C%20the%20coach%20called%20her%20to%20his%20room%20under%20a%20flimsy%20pretext.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20heard%20about%20this%20guy%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20to%20believe%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cricketer%20said%20there%20had%20been%20rumours%20and%20signs.%20During%20a%20state%20camp%2C%20before%20the%20series%20when%20the%20coach%20turned%20on%20her%2C%20a%20team%20of%20researchers%20had%20shown%20up%20at%20the%20ground%20to%20collect%20data%20about%20harassment%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20sport.%20She%20recalled%20the%20coach%E2%80%99s%20reaction.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20face%20changed%20colour%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20alerted%20everyone%20that%20that%20you%20have%20to%20say%20nothing%20of%20this%20kind%20has%20happened%E2%80%94our%20association%20is%20very%20good%2C%20facilities%20are%20good.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20coach%20called%20for%20her%20that%20night%2C%20the%20cricketer%20switched%20off%20her%20mobile%20phone%20and%20put%20her%20room%20telephone%20off%20the%20hook.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20she%20sat%20out%20the%20game%20again%20and%20fell%20back%20into%20a%20frustrating%20cycle%3A%20playing%20for%20her%20district%20well%20enough%20to%20be%20picked%20for%20the%20state%20camp%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20not%20playing%20in%20matches%E2%80%94I%20just%20sat%20out%2C%20this%20happened%20for%20three%20years.%E2%80%9D%20The%20head%20of%20her%20state%E2%80%99s%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20committee%20was%20a%20man%2C%20also%20with%20a%20dubious%20reputation.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20one%20wants%20to%20come%20out%20and%20speak%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20easy%20to%20fight%20this%20system%2C%20and%20then%20there%E2%80%99s%20your%20career.%20I%20kept%20quiet.%20I%20had%20a%20few%20years%20left%20I%20thought%20I%20should%20play.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20tried%20to%20find%20whether%20she%20could%20represent%20another%20state%2C%20she%20discovered%2C%20as%20do%20many%20young%20Indian%20junior%20cricketers%2C%20male%20or%20female%2C%20about%20another%20circle%20of%20corruption%3A%20not%20about%20sexual%20favours%2C%20but%20plain%20old%20cash%20for%20selection.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20move%20to%20another%20state%20after%20getting%20an%20NOC%20from%20my%20own%2C%20I%20was%20told%20that%20it%20was%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20play%20senior%20in%20another%20state.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20seven%20to%20ten%20lakhs%20today.%E2%80%9D%20She%20added%20that%20her%20career%20feels%20incomplete%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20waiting%20for%20WPL%20that%20it%20will%20be%20an%20opportunity%20for%20me%20but%2C%20when%20it%20came%2C%20I%20had%20to%20leave%20cricket.%20I%20feel%20very%20bad%2C%20but%20some%20things%20are%20not%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20players.%20We%20become%20helpless.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20of%20what%20stems%20from%20here%20is%20a%20twist%20of%20fate%2C%20where%20someone%E2%80%99s%20career%20is%20cut%20short%20by%20injury%20or%20a%20bad%20performance%20in%20a%20match%20where%20selectors%20were%20watching%20or%20the%20appearance%20of%20a%20talent%20greater%20than%20theirs.%20This%2C%20instead%2C%20is%20just%20an%20aspect%20of%20an%20institution%20whose%20former%20CEO%20Rahul%20Johri%20was%20let%20off%20on%20a%20sexual%20harassment%20charge%20but%20advised%20to%20attend%20gender%20sensitisation%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20the%20BCCI%20about%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Sexual%20Harrassment%20Act%2C%20which%20is%20a%20legal%20necessity%2C%20the%20response%20was%20generic.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20matter%20of%20adoption%20of%20the%20Posh%20Policy%20was%20taken%20as%20an%20agenda%20item%20in%20the%20special%20general%20meeting%20held%20on%20May%2027%2C%202023%2C%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20meeting%2C%20considering%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20a%20committee%20comprising%20Mr.%20Devajit%20Saikia%20and%20Mr.%20Ashish%20Shelar%20be%20tasked%20with%20the%20responsibility%20of%20reviewing%20the%20draft%20POSH%20policy%20considering%20both%20of%20them%20are%20eminent%20lawyers%20by%20profession.%20Accordingly%2C%20the%20POSH%20policy%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20them%20for%20review%20and%20finalisation.%20They%20are%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20finalising%20the%20POSH%20policy.%20It%20may%20be%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20BCCI%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20process%20of%20appointing%20the%20Internal%20Committee%20and%20the%20announcement%20regarding%20this%20will%20be%20made%20very%20soon.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20surge%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20in%20corrupt%20or%20badly%20functioning%20state%20associations%20has%20only%20made%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20minors%20entering%20junior%20cricket%20very%20vulnerable.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20BCCI%20has%20not%20yet%20enacted%20a%20POSH-mandated%20committee%20of%20its%20own%20nor%20brings%20down%20the%20hammer%20on%20cases%20where%20its%20state-level%20officials%20are%20accused%20of%20harassment%2C%20intimidation%20and%20bullying%20continues%20to%20give%20the%20perpetrators%20greater%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20Sharda%20Ugra%E2%80%99s%20full%20story%20on%20the%20BCCI%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fsports%2Fbjp-bcci-jay-shah%3Futm_source%3Dwire%26utm_medium%3Dexcerpt%26utm_campaign%3Dtest%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694422152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11141808%2FFo3NBAMagAEstBs.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwomens-cricket-is-rife-with-stories-of-sexual-harassment-what-is-the-bcci-doing%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20kind%20of%20wealth%20available%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20safeguards%2C%20there%20is%20no%20estimating%20what%20a%20more%20accurate%20number%20of%20cricketers%20facing%20harassment%20by%20their%20superiors%E2%80%94coaches%2C%20selectors%2C%20officials%E2%80%94may%20be.%20Women%20cricketers%20who%20have%20left%20the%20game%20are%20able%20to%20draw%20a%20clearer%20picture%2C%20but%20on%20condition%20of%20revealing%20neither%20their%20names%20nor%20the%20states%20they%20represented.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Credit%20Suisse%20case%3A%20SC%20gives%20Ajay%20Singh%20last%20chance%20to%20pay%2C%20else%20face%20jail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694420719000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-06%2F19%2Ffull%2F1655638490-7573.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcredit-suisse-case-sc-gives-ajay-singh-last-chance-to-pay-else-face-jail-123091100447_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20SpiceJet%20chairman%20Ajay%20Singh%20to%20make%20a%20payment%20of%20%24500%2C000%20towards%20an%20installment%20to%20Credit%20Suisse%20by%20September%2022%2C%20along%20with%20%241%20million%20towards%20