ess%20did%20not%20work%20out.%20They%20had%20hit%20a%20dead%20end.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20in%201997%2C%20where%20their%20baby%20girl%20was%20born%2C%20and%20Jyoti%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20being%20a%20doting%20mother.%20But%20the%20dream%20she%20harboured%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F258991%2Fcouple-quits-city-life-eco-friendly-homestay-banyan-bliss-ethnic-architecture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20a%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Udaipur%20had%20no%20intention%20of%20being%20silenced.%20%E2%80%9CIn%201999%2C%20I%20decided%20there%20was%20no%20better%20time%20than%20the%20present%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%20I%20returned%20to%20the%20land%20and%20this%20time%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20let%20go%20of%20the%20plan.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%202004%2C%20when%20Devra%20officially%20started%20welcoming%20guests%2C%20Jyoti%20would%20make%20frequent%20trips%20between%20Delhi%2C%20where%20her%20husband%20and%20child%20were%2C%20and%20Udaipur%2C%20where%20her%20dream%20was.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20years%20were%20beautiful%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20journey%20of%20inking%20relationships%20with%20the%20craftsmen%20of%20the%20city%2C%20since%20architects%20and%20civil%20engineers%20were%20tough%20to%20find%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20got%20a%20local%20person%2C%20Shivji%2C%20on%20board%2C%20and%20he%20helped%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280532%2Fchildhood-friends-convert-grandmothers-house-into-eco-friendly-homestay-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20the%20structure%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20what%20it%20is%20today.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20Shivji%E2%80%99s%20wife%2C%20Rupa%20%3Cem%3EBai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(an%20honorific%20to