%2F298965%2Fdelhi-professiors-turn-traditional-houses-into-homestays-boost-sustainable-tourism-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransform%20the%20land%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20viable%20farm%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20the%20Pichola%20Lake%20in%20Udaipur.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20bringing%20in%20soil%20from%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20While%20Jyoti%20succeeded%20in%20doing%20this%20at%20the%20time%2C%20today%20it%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20the%20Rajasthan%20Lake%20Protection%20and%20Conservation%20Authority%20passed%20a%20proposal%20that%20put%20three%20lakes%20in%20Udaipur%20under%20a%20prohibited%20zone%2C%20thus%20curbing%20desilting%20or%20soil%20extraction%20activities%20in%20them.%20Pichola%20Lake%20was%20one%20of%20these.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C20%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20ban%20that%20now%20exists%20over%20removing%20soil%20from%20the%20lake%20was%20not%20there.%20So%2C%20when%20the%20lake%20would%20dry%20up%20in%20summer%20up%20to%20its%20middle%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20quality%20loamy%20soil%20would%20be%20left%20behind.%20This%20soil%2C%20filled%20with%20minerals%20and%20nutrients%2C%20is%20perfect%20for%20growing%20plants.%20We%20started%20bringing%20it%20to%20the%20land%20to%20grow%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311053%2Fdushyant-vashisht-turned-cottage-to-sustainable-homestay-bir-terraces-uttarakhand-tourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20first%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F027f03fee490484988a3eef5325fc6e9-1694177357.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20Devra%20guests%20are%20taken%20to%20experience%20the%20local%20culture%20and%20the%20n