obius%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttarakhand%20is%20facing%20a%20severe%20crisis%20with%20heavy%20rains%20and%20flooding.%20Reports%20indicate%20that%20this%20natural%20disaster%20has%20claimed%2085%20lives%20and%20caused%20a%20loss%20of%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20in%20the%20state.%20Other%20parts%20of%20India%20are%20also%20grappling%20with%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%2C%20which%20are%20linked%20to%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202023%20%3Cem%3EIntergovernmental%20Panel%20on%20Climate%20Change%3C%2Fem%3E%20(IPCC)%20report%20stated%20that%20global%20temperatures%20have%20risen%20by%201.1%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%202011-2020%2C%20compared%20to%20what%20they%20were%20in%201850%E2%80%931900.%20The%20report%20emphasises%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294514%2Fgerman-teacher-sets-up-sustainable-dairy-farm-natural-farming-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignificance%20of%20education%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20vital%20tool%20to%20combat%20global%20warming%20and%20achieve%20sustainable%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Mobius%20Foundation%20is%20dedicated%20to%C2%A0%20contributing%20to%20sustainable%20development%20goals%20(SDGs)%20through%20various%20initiatives%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20which%20is%20the%20International%20Conference%20on%20Sustainability%20Education%20(ICSE).%20Now%20in%20its%20fifth%20year%2C%20the%20conference%20focuses%20on%20exploring%20the%20details%20and%20importance%20of%20sustainability%20education%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20change%20and%20transformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fmobius2-1694094244.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dignitaries%20at%20the%204th%20edition%20of%20ICSE%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C