20oyster%20mushrooms%20to%20traders%20in%20the%20Delhi%20market.%20Today%2C%20we%20sell%20our%20products%20across%20India%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20Pune%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Surat%20and%20Kutch%20among%20other%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20his%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20job%20to%20support%20his%20wife%E2%80%99s%20business%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20very%20risky%20decision%20as%20we%20both%20did%20not%20have%20jobs%2C%20and%20we%20had%20a%20small%20son%20to%20take%20care%20of.%20There%20were%20even%20times%20when%20we%20thought%20of%20quitting%20this%20business%20and%20returning%20to%20our%20private%20jobs%20as%20we%20were%20not%20getting%20good%20profits%20because%20of%20low%20yields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20their%20perseverance%20paid%20off%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20a%20good%20boost%20in%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290624%2Fmba-graduate-starts-mushroom-farming-during-lockdown-now-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20demand%20for%20oyster%20mushrooms%20in%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20grew.%20This%20also%20motivated%20us%20as%20we%20could%20survive%20at%20a%20time%20when%20others%20were%20losing%20their%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanjay%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20for%20Nidhi%2C%20the%20business%20helped%20her%20feel%20empowered.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20am%20not%20dependent%20on%20any%20private%20institute.%20I%20teach%20for%20my%20passion%20and%20earn%20a%20living%20through%20business.%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20establish%20something%20for%20myself.%20And%20this%20is%20something%20that%20I%20can%20pass%20on%20to%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22