al%20hospitals%2C%20it%20would%20prepare%20them%20to%20deal%20with%20healthcare%20emergencies%3B%20not%20just%20during%20COVID-19%20but%20even%20once%20the%20pandemic%20subsided.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20inception%2C%20Dr%20Edmond%20says%20the%20plan%20has%20been%20to%20increase%20the%20ICU%20capacity%20of%20hospitals%20by%2010%E2%80%9340%20beds%20through%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-surya-type-one-diabetes-awareness-for-underprivileged-kids%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekit-based%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20plan%20they%20first%20implemented%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20an%20%E2%80%9Coverwhelming%20response%E2%80%9D%20where%20they%20were%20booked%20for%20100%20beds%2C%20they%20moved%20to%20replicating%20the%20model%20in%20Maharashtra.%20Here%20the%20focus%20was%20four%20locations%20%E2%80%94%20Buldhana%2C%20Sangli%20Nanded%20and%20Jalgaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr%20Nilkant%20Bhosikar%2C%20a%20surgeon%20at%20Shri%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20Ji%20Memorial%20District%20Hospital%20in%20Nanded%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20expresses%20his%20relief%20at%20this%20new%20solution%2C%20he%20says%20he%20sees%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322528%2Futtar-pradesh-cancer-survivor-sandeep-kumar-runs-digiswasthya-free-medical-teleconsultation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimpact%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20daily%20input%20of%20many%20critical%20patients%20in%20casualty%20which%20we%20refer%20to%20GMC%20(Government%20Medical%20College)%20for%20ICU%20care.%20But%20with%20this%20facility%20here%20in%20our%20district%20hospital%2C%20patients%E2%80%99%20precious%20time%20is%20saved.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20deaths%20in%20rural%20India%20are%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20medica