ve%20a%20permanent%20home.%20By%202017%2C%20we%20were%20actively%20looking%20for%20a%20suitable%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Kartik.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYears%20later%20in%202017%2C%20at%20the%20same%20annual%20%3Cem%3Emela%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Thanedar%2C%20the%20couple%20found%20their%20dream%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20girls%20wanted%20to%20set%20up%20a%20stall%20of%20our%20jams%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emela%3C%2Fem%3E.%20One%20of%20the%20farmers%20from%20Saroga%20village%20came%20up%20to%20us%20and%20asked%20why%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20cherry%20jams.%20Jokingly%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98if%20we%20come%20to%20his%20village%20he%20would%20give%20us%20cherries%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Anuradha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20response%2C%20I%20said%20that%20we%20will%20buy%20cherries%20only%20if%20he%20gets%20us%20a%20house%20in%20his%20village.%20All%20we%20know%20is%20that%20the%20next%20day%2C%20we%20are%20driving%20up%20to%20the%20village%2C%20meeting%20the%20same%20farmer%20again%20and%20looking%20at%20the%20land%20that%20was%20to%20become%20our%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Anuradha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20pictures%20of%20the%20house%20when%20covered%20in%20snow%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fsaroga-woods-2-1-1693576393-768x401.jp